20civilian%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeography%2C%20demography%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20relentless%20air%20assault%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20contribute%20to%20the%20elevated%20death%20toll%20among%20children%2C%20experts%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%20Demographics%20and%20geography%20play%20a%20role%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%20half%20of%20Gaza's%20population%20of%202.1%20million%20are%2018%20or%20younger.%20In%20addition%20to%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20packed%20areas%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Gaza's%20terrain%20is%20mostly%20flat%2C%20increasing%20the%20effective%20range%20of%20bombs%20and%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Hamas%2C%20which%20sparked%20this%20most%20recent%20round%20of%20violence%20with%20the%20brutal%20and%20indiscriminate%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20civilians%2C%20operates%20beside%20and%20beneath%20an%20urban%20environment%20from%20which%20it%20is%20exceedingly%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20for%20residents%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Israeli%20strategy%20of%20assailing%20Gaza%20with%20wave%20after%20wave%20of%20airstrikes%20is%20also%20to%20blame%2C%20according%20to%20Omar%20Shakir%2C%20the%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20director%20at%20Human%20Rights%20Watch.%20Sheltering%20in%20UN-operated%20refugee%20camps%2C%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20creates%20risks%20for%20more%20civilian%20casualties%20because%20people%20are%20congregated%20in%20areas%20under%20attack%2C%20Shakir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intensity%20of%20the%20bombardment%20they've%20carried%20out%20carries%20a%20foreseeable%20risk%20to%20civilian%20harm%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakir%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20that%20at%20a%20different%20degree%20of%20intensity.%20The%20significant%20death%20toll%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20intense%20type%20of%20bombardment.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palestinian%20children%20walking%20by%20a%2