5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fisrael-war-hamas-gaza-rafah-airstrike-kills-civilans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinued%20to%20target%3C%2Fa%3E%20southern%20Gaza%20after%20the%20evacuation%20order.%20Among%20the%20victims%20were%20the%20son%20and%20grandson%20of%20Al%20Jazeera%20Arabic's%20Gaza%20bureau%20chief%2C%20who%20died%20in%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20October%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaza%20is%20already%20crowded%2C%20and%20Israel's%20evacuation%20orders%20have%20packed%20the%20civilian%20population%20into%20even%20smaller%20areas.%20Much%20of%20the%20disproportionate%20effect%20on%20children%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20offense%20in%20this%20shrinking%2C%20overcrowded%20space%2C%20according%20to%20Shakir%2C%20HRW's%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20director.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael%20says%20its%20attacks%20are%20highly%20regulated%20and%20reviewed%20by%20lawyers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20said%20they%20are%20adhering%20to%20the%20Law%20of%20Armed%20Conflict%2C%20which%20requires%20combatants%20to%20balance%20military%20necessity%20against%20the%20protection%20of%20civilian%20life.%20The%20IDF%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20highly-regulated%2C%20multi-tiered%20process%20for%20approving%20pre-planned%20attacks%20against%20military%20objectives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20wrote.%20Military%20lawyers%20%26quot%3Bare%20on%20hand%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20command%20to%20ensure%20that%20strikes%20comply%20with%20international%20legal%20obligations%2C%20including%20proportionality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF's%20professed%20adherence%20to%20international%20law%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20statements%20made%20during%20the%20conflict%20by%20Israel's%20political%20leaders%2C%20who%20have%20promised%20to%20deliver%20no-holds-barred%20vengeance%20for%20the%20Hamas%20attacks.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20cripple%20them%20mercilessly%20and%20avenge%20this%20black%20day%20they%20have%20brought%20upon%20Israel%20and%20its%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%20%26quot%3BResidents%20of%20Gaza%2C%20get%20out%20now.%20We%20will%20be%20everywhere%20and%20with%20all%20our%20might.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoav%20Gallant%2C%20Israel's%20Minister%20of%20Defense%2C%20said%20he%20was%20removing%20%26quot%3Ball%20restraints%26quot%3B%20from%20Israel's%20response%20and%20characterized%20his%20targets%20as%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20animals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20entire%20nation%20out%20there%20that%20is%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20true%20this%20rhetoric%20about%20civilians%20not%20aware%2C%20not%20involved.%20It's%20absolutely%20not%20true.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHerzog%20later%20said%20he%20did%20not%20mean%20to%20imply%20that%20Palestinian%20civilians%20were%20legitimate%20targets.%20Nevertheless%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20IDF%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.co.il%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F2023-10-10%2Fty-article-live%2F0000018b-1645-d465-abbb-16f71d060000%231720386730%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20airstrikes%20on%20Gaza%20would%20prioritize%20%26quot%3Bdamage%2C%20not%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20email%2C%20Insider%20asked%20the%20IDF%20spokesperson%20whether%20Israel%20had%20imposed%20any%20special%20measures%20to%20protect%20the%20lives%20of%20children.%20The%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20Israel%20was%20operating%20%26quot%3Bin%20stark%20contrast%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BHamas'%20barbaric%20attacks.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20IDF%20follows%20international%20law%20and%20takes%20feasible%20precautions%20to%20mitigate%20civilian%20harm%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%2C%20without%20providing%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20has%20been%20investigating%20Israel%20for%20war%20crimes%20since%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20Criminal%20Court%20Prosecutor%20Karim%20A.A.%20Khan%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Israel%2C%20by%20impeding%20aid%2C%20could%20be%20investigated%20for%20war%20crimes.%20Collective%20punishment%20and%20starving%20civilians%20are%20both%20banned%20by%20the%20laws%20of%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20alarming%20to%20see%20the%20bodies%20of%20young%20children%20that%20could%20be%20our%20own%20children%20being%20dragged%2C%20baked%20in%20dust%2C%20still%2C%20silent%2C%20motionless%20because%20they're%20dead%20%E2%80%94%20or%20with%20injuries%20and%20blood%20%E2%80%94%20being%20rushed%20to%20medical%20facilities%20that%20may%20not%20have%20the%20means%20to%20fix%20them%20and%20give%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20breathe%20the%20air%20and%20see%20the%20sun%20of%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20said%20in%20Cairo.%20Khan's%20remarks%20appeared%20to%20suggest%20that%20Hamas%20as%20well%20as%20Israel%20could%20potentially%20find%20themselves%20prosecuted%20by%20the%20ICC.%20Since%202019%2C%20the%20court%20has%20had%20an%20open%20investigation%20into%20potential%20Israeli%20war%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20death%20toll%2C%20disabling%20injuries%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bundignified%26quot%3B%20ways%20in%20which%20children's%20families%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20neighbors%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20will%20also%20cause%20surviving%20children%20deep%20psychological%20trauma%20and%20physical%20pain%2C%20according%20to%20senior%20Palestine%20analyst%20at%20the%20International%20Crisis%20Group%2C%20Tahani%20Mustafa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20seeing%20their%20entire%20world%20get%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mustafa%20said.%20Given%20the%20blockade%20imposed%20by%20Israel%2C%20which%20for%20a%20time%20completely%C2%A0%20stopped%20the%20flow%20of%20food%20and%20water%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20cut%20off%20fuel%20from%20entering%20into%20Gaza%2C%20children%20are%20also%20witnessing%20the%20way%20they%20have%20had%20to%20store%20bodies%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaza-ice-cream-trucks-store-bodies-cemeteries-morgues-capacity-2023-10%5C%22%3Ein%20ice%20cream%20trucks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20kind%20of%20trauma%20and%20violence%2C%20Mustafa%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20nothing%20for%20political%20inclination%20for%20these%20young%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20many%20Palestinians%20who%20have%20taken%20up%20arms%20against%20Israelis%20%26quot%3Bhave%20been%20victims%20of%20these%20sorts%20of%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20Mustafa%20said.%20%26quot%3BNever%20mind%20the%20deep%20psychological%20trauma%20and%20physical%20pain.%20Politically%2C%20this%20serves%20neither%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbandoning%20'roof%20knocks'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20past%20Gaza%20offensives%2C%20Israel%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F07%2F09%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fby-phone-and-leaflet-israeli-attackers-warn-gazans.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esometimes%20warned%3C%2Fa%3E%20civilians%20inside%20targeted%20buildings%20with%20phone%20calls%2C%20leaflets%2C%20or%20by%20deploying%20low-yield%20munitions%20on%20buildings%20in%20advance%20of%20a%20major%20strike%2C%20a%20practice%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Broof%20knocking.%26quot%3B%20An%20IDF%20officer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F10%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fgaza-israel-airstrikes.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20was%20too%20busy%20dropping%20bombs%20on%20targets%20to%20use%20the%20tactic%20this%20time.%20Instead%20of%20roof%20knocks%2C%20Israel%20is%20issuing%20mass%20evacuation%20orders%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Flive%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-updates-week-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflyers%20stating%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Banyone%20who%20is%20near%20Hamas%20fighters%20will%20put%20their%20lives%20in%20danger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20volume%20of%20the%20current%20bombing%20campaign%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20lack%20of%20specific%20warnings%2C%20has%20killed%20far%20more%20children%20and%20at%20a%20much%20faster%20rate%20than%20previous%20Israeli%20offensives%20in%20Gaza.%20During%20Operation%20Protective%20Edge%2C%20in%202014%2C%20521%20out%20of%20the%201%2C483%20civilians%20killed%20were%20children%20%E2%80%94%2035%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20150725191044%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent.aspx%3Fid%3D1010361%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20United%20Nations.%20That%20campaign%20went%20on%20for%2050%20days.%20Already%2C%20operating%20on%20the%20same%20terrain%2C%20the%20current%20Israeli%20offensive%20has%20killed%20more%20than%20six%20times%20the%20number%20of%20children%20in%20roughly%20half%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELila%20Hassan%20is%20a%20freelance%20investigative%20reporter%20covering%20extremism%20and%20immigration.%20She%20can%20be%20reached%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3ALila%40lila-hassan.com%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22mailto%3ALila%40lila-hassan.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3ELila%40lila-hassan.com%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMattathias%20Schwartz%20is%20chief%20national%20security%20correspondent%20at%20Insider.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aschwartz79%40protonmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschwa