tment%20opportunity%20in%20stocks%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20coming%20pop%20in%20corporate%20profits%20across%20sectors%20of%20the%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20investment%20firm%20Richard%20Bernstein%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20view%20has%20been%20that%20the%20economy%20isn't%20actually%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20RBA%20said%20in%20a%20note%20Tuesday%2C%20pointing%20to%20fears%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-economy-recession-bankruptcies-unemployment-bubble-societe-generale-2023-10%5C%22%3Eeconomy%20could%20be%20headed%20for%20a%20hard%20landing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20a%20coming%20recession.%20%26quot%3BFurthering%20the%20airplane%20metaphor%2C%20we%20see%20profits%20taking%20off%20%E2%80%A6Corporate%20profits%20are%20accelerating%20and%20the%20overall%20economy%20looks%20set%20to%20remain%20quite%20healthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20global%20stocks%20tipped%20into%20a%20profits%20recession%20this%20year%2C%20earnings%20appear%20to%20have%20troughed%2C%20RBA%20said%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20is%20expecting%20profits%20to%20accelerate%20into%20the%20end%20of%202023%20and%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20leading%20indicators%20for%20corporate%20profits%20have%20also%20bottomed%2C%20which%20suggest%20that%20earnings%20will%20gain%20momentum%20into%20next%20year.%20The%20firm%20see%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20earnings%20growth%20to%20pick%20up%2010%25-15%25%20through%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20growth%20trends%20are%20supported%20by%20a%20highly%20robust%20economy.%20Before%20adjusting%20for%20inflation%2C%20GDP%20grew%20a%20whopping%208.5%25%20the%20past%20quarter%2C%20the%20highest%20pace%20of%20nominal%20growth%20seen%20since%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20growth%20already%20appears%20to%20be%20showing%20up%20in%20corporate%20earnings.%20There%20are%20around%20130%20US%20firms%20that%20have%20reported%20at%20least%2025%25%20earnings%20growth%20as%20of%20October%2C%20according%20to%20an%20RBA%20analysis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProfits%20could%20jump%20in%20nearly%20every%20area%20of%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20the%20firm%20predicted%2C%20apart%20from%20companies%20among%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%2C%20which%20have%20seen%20shares%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsp500-spx-magnificent-7-tech-stocks-artificial-intelligence-nvda-tsla-2023-9%5C%22%3Esoar%20this%20year%20already%20on%20Wall%20Street's%20enthusiasm%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20now%2C%20those%20megacap%20tech%20giants%20are%20overvalued%2C%20RBA%20said%2C%20which%20makes%20virtually%20any%20other%20bet%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20narrow%20leadership%20seems%20totally%20unjustified%20and%20their%20extreme%20valuations%20suggest%20a%20once-in-a-generation%20investment%20opportunity%20in%20virtually%20anything%20other%20than%20those%207%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20market%20forecasters%20have%20made%20a%20bullish%20case%20for%20stocks%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20despite%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20set%20to%20end%20October%20with%20a%20third%20consecutive%20monthly%20loss.%20That%20decline%20has%20largely%20been%20sparked%20by%20surging%20bond%20yields%20and%20fears%20of%20higher-for-longer%20interest%20rates%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20though%20there%20are%20some%20signs%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-year-end-rally-2024-forecast-fed-2023-10%5C%22%3Eequities%20could%20quickly%20rebound%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20recent%20correction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-buying-opportunity-economy-bull-market-profits-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698780