n%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20perhaps%20someone%20played%20a%20prank%20on%20the%20Opposition%20leaders.%20They%20should%20lodge%20an%20official%20complaint%20and%20the%20Government%20will%20take%20appropriate%20action%20on%20that%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20is%20going%20through%20a%20weak%20phase%2C%20thus%20they%20see%20conspiracy%20in%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Opposition%20is%20going%20through%20a%20very%20weak%20phase%20these%20days%2C%20so%20they%20see%20conspiracy%20in%20everything.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20Apple%20has%20itself%20cleared%20that%20this%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20malfunction%20and%20this%20message%20has%20reached%20people%20in%20150%20countries.%20It%20seems%20that%20this%20was%20an%20error%20from%20Apple's%20end%2C%20hackers%20too%20are%20active%20across%20the%20world.%20This%20will%20be%20investigated.%20Apple%20too%20has%20been%20told%20to%20join%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Opposition)%20can%20claim%20anything%20they%20want%20but%20the%20country%20knows%20their%20situation%2C%20they%20are%20so%20tangled%20in%20their%20infighting.%20They%20should%20look%20at%20their%20weaknesses%20first%20instead%20of%20commenting%20on%20us.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20government%20has%20no%20role%20in%20this%20and%20the%20government%20doesn't%20need%20to%20do%20anything%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Congress%20national%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20party's%20General%20Secretary%20organisation%20KC%20Venugopal%20also%20received%20the%20%26quot%3BApple%20warning%20message%26quot%3B%20on%20their%20phone%20on%20Tuesday%20along%20with%20other%20opposition%20leaders%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E