0according%20to%20the%20Apple%20support%20page%20on%20its%20website%2C%20State-sponsored%20attacks%20are%20highly%20complex%2C%20cost%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20develop%2C%20and%20often%20have%20a%20short%20shelf%20life.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20users%20will%20never%20be%20targeted%20by%20such%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20says%20if%20it%20discovers%20activity%20consistent%20with%20a%20state-sponsored%20attack%2C%20it%20will%20notify%20the%20targeted%20users%20in%20two%20ways.%20A%20Threat%20Notification%20will%20be%20displayed%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20page%20after%20the%20user%20has%20signed%20in%20to%20appleid.apple.com.%20Additionally%2C%20Apple%20will%20send%20an%20email%20and%20iMessage%20notification%20to%20the%20email%20addresses%20and%20phone%20numbers%20associated%20with%20the%20user's%20Apple%20ID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698776460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fsqn1q1do_piyush-goyal_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-someone-pranked-opposition-leaders-minister-piyush-goyal-on-hacking-row-4533250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20on%20Tuesday%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20in%20connection%20with%20Apple's%20'state-sponsored%20attack'%20message%20to%20some%20Opposition%20leaders%20and%20said%20that%20someone%20might%20have%20played%20a%20prank%20on%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-someone-pranked-opposition-leaders-minister-piyush-goyal-on-hacking-row-4533250%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-someone-pranked-opposition-leaders-minis