%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla%20Wins%201st%20US%20Suit%20That%20Blamed%20Its%20Autopilot%20Feature%20For%20Fatal%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20on%20Tuesday%20won%20the%20first%20US%20trial%20over%20allegations%20that%20its%20Autopilot%20driver%20assistant%20feature%20led%20to%20a%20death%2C%20a%20major%20victory%20for%20the%20automaker%20as%20it%20faces%20several%20other%20similar%20lawsuits%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20in%20a%20California%20state%20court%2C%20was%20filed%20by%20two%20passengers%20in%20a%202019%20crash%20who%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20knowing%20Autopilot%20was%20defective%20when%20it%20sold%20the%20car.%20Tesla%20argued%20human%20error%20caused%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2012-member%20jury%20on%20Tuesday%20announced%20they%20found%20the%20vehicle%20did%20not%20have%20a%20manufacturing%20defect.%20The%20verdict%20came%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20deliberations%2C%20and%20the%20vote%20was%209-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Tesla%20and%20the%20plaintiffs%20did%20not%20immediately%20comment%20on%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20lawsuit%20alleged%20the%20Autopilot%20system%20caused%20owner%20Micah%20Lee's%20Model%203%20to%20suddenly%20veer%20off%20a%20highway%20east%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20at%2065%20miles%20per%20hour%20(105%20km%20per%20hour)%2C%20strike%20a%20palm%20tree%20and%20burst%20into%20flames%2C%20all%20in%20the%20span%20of%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20crash%20killed%20Lee%20and%20seriously%20injured%20his%20two%20passengers%2C%20including%20a%20then-8-year-old%20boy%20who%20was%20disemboweled%2C%20court%20documents%20show.%20The%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20against%20Tesla%20by%20the%20passengers%2C%20accuses%20the%20company%20of%20knowing%20that%20Autopilot%20and%20other%20safety%20systems%20were%20defective%20when%20it%20sold%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETesla%20denied%20liability%2C%20saying%20Lee%20consumed%20alcohol%20before%20getting%20behind%20the%20wheel.%20The%20electric-vehicle%20maker%20also%20claims%20it%20was%20unclear%20whether%20Autopilot%20was%20engaged%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20been%20testing%20and%20rolling%20out%20its%20Autopilot%20and%20more%20advanced%20Full%20Self-Driving%20(FSD)%20system%2C%20which%20Chief%20Executive%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20touted%20as%20crucial%20to%20his%20company's%20future%20but%20which%20has%20drawn%20regulatory%20and%20legal%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETesla%20won%20an%20earlier%20trial%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20in%20April%20with%20a%20strategy%20of%20saying%20that%20it%20tells%20drivers%20that%20its%20technology%20requires%20human%20monitoring%2C%20despite%20the%20%26quot%3BAutopilot%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFull%20Self-Driving%26quot%3B%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20case%20was%20about%20an%20accident%20where%20a%20Model%20S%20swerved%20into%20the%20curb%20and%20injured%20its%20driver%2C%20and%20jurors%20told%20Reuters%20after%20the%20verdict%20that%20they%20believed%20Tesla%20warned%20drivers%20about%20its%20system%20and%20driver%20distraction%20was%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698775140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fs6dijfpc_tesla-logo-reuters_625x300_29_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftesla-wins-autopilot-trial-involving-fatal-crash-4533143%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20on%20Tuesday%20won%20the%20first%20US%20trial%20over%20allegations%20that%20its%20Autopilot%20driver%20assistant%20feature%20led%20to%20a%20death%2C%20a%20major%20victory%20for%20the%20automaker%20as%20it%20faces%20several%20other%20similar%20lawsuits%20across%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalU