trapped%20Pakistan%20is%20navigating%20record%20inflation%20and%20a%20tough%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20bailout%20program%2C%20the%20officials%20in%20the%20country%20have%20accused%20the%20undocumented%20migrants%20of%20draining%20the%20resources%20for%20decades.%20Islamabad%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20many%20bombings%20in%20the%20country%20this%20year%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20Afghan%20nationals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20two%20opinions%20that%20we%20are%20attacked%20from%20within%20Afghanistan%20and%20Afghan%20nationals%20are%20involved%20in%20attacks%20on%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bugti%20said%20in%20a%20news%20conference.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20do%20not%20go%2C%20...%20then%20all%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20the%20provinces%20or%20federal%20government%20will%20be%20utilised%20to%20deport%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bugti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20illegal%20immigrants%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20voluntarily%20leave%20the%20country%20will%20be%20helped%20by%20the%20nation.%20But%20authorities%20also%20warned%20that%20anyone%20found%20in%20the%20country%20illegally%20after%20Wednesday%20would%20be%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%20also%20stated%20that%20the%201.4%20million%20Afghans%20who%20are%20registered%20refugees%20need%20not%20worry.%20It%20denied%20targeting%20Afghan%20nationals%20and%20said%20that%20the%20focus%20is%20only%20on%20people%20who%20are%20in%20the%20country%20illegally%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20nationality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EDeportation%20centres%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20three%20deportation%20centres%20have%20been%20set%20up%20in%20southwestern%20Baluchistan.%20Another%20three%20centres%20have%20also%20been%20set%20in%20northwest%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%20More%20than%2060%2C000%20Afghans%20have%20returned%20home%20since%20the%20crackdown%20was%20announced%2C%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20the%20caretaker%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20northwest%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EPakistan's%20crackdown%20condemned%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20diplomats%20and%20representatives%20have%20condemned%20Pakistan's%20crackdown%20on%20immigrants.%20Afghanistan%20has%20called%20Pakistan's%20move%20%26quot%3Bharassment%26quot%3B.%20The%20Afghan%20embassy%20in%20Islamabad%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20said%20more%20than%201%2C000%20Afghans%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%20-%20half%20of%20them%20despite%20having%20a%20legal%20right%20to%20be%20in%20Pakistan.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20repeated%20promises%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20authorities%2C%20the%20arrest%20and%20harassment%20of%20Afghan%20refugees%20by%20the%20police%20in%20Pakistan%20continues%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20a%20group%20of%20former%20US%20diplomats%20and%20representatives%20of%20resettlement%20organisations%20also%20urged%20Pakistan%20not%20to%20deport%20Afghans%20awaiting%20US%20visas%20under%20a%20program%20that%20resettled%20vulnerable%20refugees%20fleeing%20Taliban%20rule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20also%20made%20a%20similar%20appeal%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20crackdown%20could%20lead%20to%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20including%20the%20separation%20of%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698773100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fq87a5q1_afghan-migrants_625x300_31_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-to-expel-over-a-million-illegal-migrants-after-november-1-heres-why-4533119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20has%20asked%20all%20undocumented%20immigrants%2C%20including%20an%20estimated%201.7%20million%20Afghans%2C%20to%20voluntarily%20leav