re-wind-industry-is-in-doldrums%2Farticleshow%2F104864072.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplainer-why-us-offshore-wind-industry-is-in-doldrums%2Famp_articleshow%2F104864072.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplainer-why-us-offshore-wind-industry-is-in-doldrums%2Famp_articleshow%2F104864072.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Behaviour%20on%20the%20World%20Stage%20Is%20Not%20Helping%20Its%20Interests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26083945%2FF6NVFb_XAAAuHrW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20abstained%20from%20calling%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20a%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20upsetting%20the%20United%20States.%20India%20was%20told%20by%20the%20new%20Maldives%20leader%20to%20remove%20our%20soldiers%20from%20that%20country.%20Qatar%20sentenced%20eight%20Navy%20veterans%20to%20death.%20Sri%20Lanka%20allowed%20a%20Chinese%20spy%20ship%20to%20dock%20in%20Colombo%20despite%20India%E2%80%99s%20objections.%20Bhutan%20has%20said%20it%20was%20about%20to%20conclude%20boundary%20negotiations%20with%20China%2C%20including%20on%20Doklam.%20Nepal%20cannot%20use%20its%20new%20Gautam%20Buddha%20airport%20because%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20overflight%20of%20large%20planes.%20Canada%20has%20said%20it%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20normalise%20visas%20for%20Indians%20till%202024.%20These%20things%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20space%20of%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20South%20Asian%20nations%20except%20India%20voted%20to%20end%20the%20violence%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Bhutan%2C%20which%20traditionally%20votes%20with%20India.%20The%2070%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20in%20the%20Maldives%20who%20will%20now%20return%20maintain%20radar%20stations%20and%20surveillance%20aircraft%2C%20and%20Indian%20warships%20help%20patrol%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20exclusive%20economic%20zone.%20The%20reason%20we%20have%20been%20told%20to%20go%20is%20that%20the%20Maldives%20wants%20to%20favour%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhether%20we%20are%20running%20a%20successful%20foreign%20policy%2C%20as%20fans%20of%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20believe%2C%20or%20we%20are%20ruining%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20reputation%2C%20as%20some%20of%20us%20think%20we%20are%20doing%2C%20is%20not%20important%20to%20debate.%20This%20is%20because%20views%20are%20set%20in%20stone%20since%20we%20are%20in%20the%20tenth%20year%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20years%20and%20there%20is%20sufficient%20evidence%20to%20convince%20someone%20one%20way%20or%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%20interesting%20is%20to%20examine%20what%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20actually%20is%20and%20what%20it%20is%20intended%20to%20achieve.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20said%20it%20would%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20SAARC%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20states%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20encouraged%20to%20play%20a%20greater%20role%20in%20diplomacy%E2%80%9D.%20For%20instance%2C%20Punjab%2C%20which%20overwhelmingly%20suffers%20when%20Canadian%20visas%20are%20affected%2C%20would%20caution%20New%20Delhi%20on%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20both%20these%20references%20were%20eliminated.%20No%20fresh%20text%20replaced%20it%20but%20those%20who%20study%20foreign%20policy%20praised%20a%20new%20approach%20that%20they%20saw%20coming%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20comes%20from%20a%20series%20of%20speeches%20made%20by%20Subrahmanyam%20Jaishankar%20on%20things%20as%20diverse%20as%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise%20to%20power%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20lost%20decades%2C%20the%20Mahabharata%2C%20maritime%20power%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20assorted%20speeches%20were%20compiled%20into%20a%20book%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3EThe%20India%20Way%3A%20Strategies%20for%20an%20Uncertain%20World%3C%2Fem%3E.%20What%20are%20these%20strategies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Jaishankar%20assumes%20that%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20will%20continue%20to%20look%20inward%20(his%20book%20was%20published%20just%20before%20Donald%20Trump%20lost%20the%202020%20election)%2C%20while%20China%20would%20continue%20to%20rise.%20This%20would%20open%20the%20space%20for%20countries%20like%20India%20to%20be%20opportunistic%20in%20their%20engagements%20with%20the%20world%20and%20they%20did%20not%20need%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20India%20wanted%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmulti-polar%20Asia%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20one%20in%20which%20India%20could%20claim%20parity%20with%20China.%20Many%20balls%20would%20need%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20air%20(Jaishankar%20has%20a%20fondness%20for%20stock%20phrases)%20and%20India%20would%20handle%20them%20with%20dexterity.%20This%20was%20opportunism%2C%20but%20that%20was%20all%20right%20because%20opportunism%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20culture.%20The%20Mahabharata%E2%80%99s%20lessons%2C%20Jaishankar%20says%2C%20are%20that%20deceit%20and%20immorality%20are%20merely%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20play%20by%20the%20rules%E2%80%9D.%20Drona%E2%80%99s%20demanding%20of%20Eklavya%E2%80%99s%20thumb%2C%20Indra%E2%80%99s%20appropriation%20of%20Karna%E2%80%99s%20armour%2C%20Arjuna%20using%20Shikhandi%20as%20a%20human%20shield%2C%20these%20were%20but%20%E2%80%9Cpractices%20and%20traditions%E2%80%9D.%20Inconsistency%20in%20policy%20was%20not%20only%20fine%20but%20required%20because%20%E2%80%9Cobsessing%20about%20consistency%E2%80%9D%20made%20little%20sense%20in%20changing%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20was%20such%20a%20doctrine%20to%20be%20called%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20he%20made%20where%20he%20first%20laid%20out%20this%20doctrine%20of%20opportunism%20and%20inconsistency%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20give%20it%20a%20name.%20He%20takes%20up%20and%20discards%20the%20phrases%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cmulti-alignment%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9Csounds%20too%20opportunistic%E2%80%9D)%20and%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20first%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9Csounds%20self-centred%E2%80%9D).%20He%20settles%20at%20%E2%80%9Cadvancing%20prosperity%20and%20influence%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20he%20says%20is%20accurate%20but%20admits%20is%20not%20catchy.%20He%20believes%20that%20some%20name%20will%20eventually%20come%20if%20it%20is%20pursued%20long%20enough%2C%20because%20part%20of%20the%20challenge%20is%20that%20we%20are%20still%20in%20the%20early%20phase%20of%20a%20major%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20that%20is%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20that%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20name%20for%20it%20as%20clean%20and%20understandable%20as%2C%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnon-alignment%E2%80%9D%2C%20could%20be%20that%20this%20was%20no%20real%20foreign%20policy%20at%20all.%20The%20problems%20that%20have%20been%20listed%20at%20the%20top%20of%20this%20article%20reflect%20this%20lack%20of%20coherence%20and%20effectiveness.%20Buying%20cheap%20Russian%20oil%20when%20nobody%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20doing%20so%20is%20not%20a%20foreign%20policy%2C%20but%20it%20was%20praised%20as%20being%20that.%20A%20rotating%20presidency%20of%20the%20G-20%20was%20not%20an%20achievement%2C%20but%20that%20is%20how%20it%20was%20sold%20to%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20interested%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20and%20what%20made%20for%20pageant%20and%20ceremony%2C%20was%20being%20passed%20off%20as%20something%20meaningful.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20escape%20the%20conclusion%20that%20Jaishankar%20provided%20the%20sophistry%20to%20cover%20what%20was%20essentially%20random%20and%20directionless%20behaviour%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20passing%20off%20as%20foreign%20policy%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20says%20that%20this%20nameless%20policy%20of%20his%20is%20intended%20to%20achieve%20four%20outcomes.%20Greater%20prosperity%20at%20home%3B%20peace%20on%20the%20borders%3B%20protection%20of%20Indians%20and%20enhanced%20influence%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20going%20through%20what%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20borders%20or%20on%20prosperity.%20The%20issue%20is%20whether%20having%20examined%20what%20we%20have%20tried%20to%20achieve%20and%20looking%20at%20what%20results%20around%20us%2C%20we%20should%20reassess%20what%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20world%20is%20and%20whether%20we%20are%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20for%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698770719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26083945%2FF6NVFb_XAAAuHrW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findias-behaviour-on-the-world-stage-is-not-helping-its-interests%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20actually%20is%20and%20what%20it%20is%20intended%20to%20achieve%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findias-behaviour-on-the-world-stage-is-not-helping-its-interests%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunny%20on%20Kennedy%20getting%20standing%20ovation%20at%20MAMI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698770427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104864224%2Cimgsize-36232.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsunny-leone-reacts-to-kennedy-receiving-a-standing-ovation-at-mami-i-am-happy-that-people-like-my-character%2Farticleshow%2F104864219.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F1048