on%20that%3F%20Also%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20said%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20kin%20of%20a%20government%E2%80%99s%20head%20has%20applied%20for%20an%20elected%20post%20at%20the%20WHO%20or%20even%20any%20other%20UN%20agency.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20answer%20your%20first%20part%2C%20I%20do%20have%20a%20personal%20opinion%20but%20I%20will%20give%20it%20a%20pass%20because%20it%20is%20against%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20%5Bof%20the%20WHO%20elections%5D%20to%20make%20such%20personal%20comments.%20On%20the%20second%20part%2C%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12140159%2FF6jsHPjacAA7LFS.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12140159%2FF6jsHPjacAA7LFS.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12140159%2FF6jsHPjacAA7LFS-300x200.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20and%20Saima%20Wazed%20with%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Jill%20Biden.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40drSaimaWazed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20SEAR%20has%20the%20highest%20burden%20of%20many%20diseases.%20Also%2C%20it%20is%20home%20to%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20undernourishment%20and%20these%20challenges%20make%20the%20region%20different%20from%20others.%20How%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20address%20them%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20circumstances%20exist%20because%20we%20%5BSEAR%20region%5D%20have%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20entire%20population.%20That%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20why%20we%