e%20of%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20SEAR%20Office%20in%20enhancing%20access%20to%20health%20when%2C%20essentially%2C%20it%20is%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20provide%20that%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20can%20provide%20the%20necessary%20guidelines%20and%20policy%20advice%20to%20the%20governments.%20We%20need%20to%20build%20on%20this%20through%20advocacy%20with%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20you%20remodel%20your%20dialogue%20for%20this%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20will%20say%20is%20that%20the%20budgets%2C%20or%20health%20expenditures%2C%20should%20not%20be%20just%20viewed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98cost%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20government.%20It%20should%20be%20viewed%20as%20an%20investment%20in%20human%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20this%20region%2C%20and%20especially%20in%20India%2C%20access%20to%20health%20is%20not%20the%20only%20issue.%20Even%20the%20quality%20of%20healthcare%20being%20provided%20is%20also%20an%20issue.%20How%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20address%20that%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20and%20largely%20the%20SEAR%2C%20provides%20good%20quality%20tertiary-level%20healthcare%2C%20and%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20medical%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20we%20also%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20%5Bthe%20quality%20of%5D%20primary%20and%20secondary%20level%20healthcare%2C%20%5Bin%20peripheral%20areas%20and%20small%20towns%5D.%20We%20should%20have%20a%20quality%20workforce%20there%20along%20with%20medicines%20and%20diagnostics.%20The%20majority%20of%20services%20can%20be%20given%20at%20the%20two%20lower%20levels%20of%20healthcare%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20WHO%20representative%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20political%20leadership%20in%20this%20direction.%20Different%20member%20states%20of%20the%20SEAR%20can%20learn%20from%20each%20other%2C%20too%2C%20in%20providing%20primary%20healthcare.%20Your%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20programme%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDespite%20so%20many%20reports%20and%20various%20engagements%20at%20all%20levels%20between%20non-governmental%20organisations%20and%20the%20government%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20expenditure%20on%20healthcare%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20lowest.%20Where%20do%20you%20think%20things%20went%20wrong%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20has%20reached%202.5%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20and%20I%20think%20it%20is%20an%20increment%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Feconomicsurvey%2Fdoc%2Feschapter%2Fechap06.pdf%5C%22%3EEconomic%20Survey%202022-23%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20figures%20are%20available%20for%202021-22.%20For%20that%20year%2C%20the%20central%20and%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20combined%20expenditure%20on%20health%20was%201.6%25%20only.%20The%20revised%20estimates%20for%20FY%2022%20stand%20at%202.2%25%20but%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20would%20be%20available%20only%20next%20year.%20Since%202014%2C%20health%20expenditure%20has%20steadily%20risen%2C%20you%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20do%20you%20compare%20it%20with%202014%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20there%20has%20been%20a%20steady%20rise%20%5Bin%20health%20expenditure%5D%20from%202014.%20%5BAccording%20to%20the%20last%20Economic%20Survey%2C%20health%20expenditure%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20GDP%20in%202015-16%2C%202016-17%2C%202017-18%2C%202018-19%2C%202019-20%20and%202020-21%20was%201.3%25%2C%201.4%25.%201.4%25%2C%201.4%25%2C%201.4%25%20and%201.6%25%2C%20respectively.%20The%20actual%20expenditure%20figures%20are%20only%20available%20till%202020-21.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20a%20few%20others%2C%20too%2C%20lay%20a%20lot%20of%20stress%20on%20insurance-based%20health%20financing%20models%20while%20some%20others%20feel%20that%20creating%20a%20health%20infrastructure%20is%20better.%20What%20is%20your%20opinion%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20there%20can%20be%20a%20scenario%20of%20one%20versus%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20model%20is%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20France%2C%20etc.%2C%20where%20each%20and%20every%20citizen%20will%20have%20access%20to%20health%20services%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20other%20one%20is%20about%20health%20insurance%2C%20in%20which%20you%20talk%20about%20pooling%20resources%20from%20each%20individual%2C%20cross-subsidising%20from%20the%20rich%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20helping%20the%20latter%20through%20insurance.%20That%20has%20worked%20well%20in%20countries%20like%20Germany%20and%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20Thailand%20spends%20a%20lot%20on%20healthcare.%20Unlike%20India%2C%20where%20only%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Firis.who.int%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F10665%2F352685%2F9789290229049-eng.pdf%3Fsequence%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Eone-third%20of%20the%20health%20expenditure%20comes%20from%20the%20government%2C%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20in%20Thailand%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20share%20is%20two-thirds.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20idea%20is%20to%20finance%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20people%20are%20not%20pushed%20into%20poverty%20due%20to%20expenses%20incurred%20on%20healthcare.%20Countries%20like%20Japan%20and%20Thailand%20also%20took%2040%20to%2050%20years%20to%20achieve%20the%20best%20of%20their%20health%20financing%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYou%20spoke%20about%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20programme.%20But%20there%20is%20also%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20criticism%20against%20it%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20cover%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20population.%20And%20recently%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ECAG%20report%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20highlighted%20large-scale%20corruption.%20Do%20you%20still%20believe%20it%20is%20the%20panacea%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20health%20problems%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20mean%2C%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20say%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20panacea%20or%20not%2C%20but%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20is%20that%20covering%20500%20million%20people%20%5Bunder%20the%20programme%5D%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20that%20we%20know%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20is%20a%20great%20achievement.%20So%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20India%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20cover%20more.%20Everyone%20gradually%20will%20be%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThough%20the%20government%2C%20so%20far%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20made%20public%20any%20such%20intention%20of%20covering%20the%20entire%20population%2C%20the%20programme%20is%20also%20criticised%20for%20having%20diverted%20its%20attention%20from%20creating%20better%20health%20facilities%20to%20investing%20in%20insurance%20schemes%20as%20a%20proxy%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20mixing%20two%20things%20here.%20Insurance%20is%20essential%20for%20providing%20income%20to%20health%20facilities.%20And%20once%20there%20is%20income%2C%20infrastructure%20and%20various%20issues%20can%20be%20improved.%20Infrastructure%20does%20not%20exist%20in%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20government%20can%20still%20invest%20in%20infrastructure%20%5Bwhile%20funding%20insurance-based%20programmes%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15203438%2FSurgical-ward-at-Churachandpur-hospital-II.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15203438%2FSurgical-ward-at-Churachandpur-hospital-II.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15203438%2FSurgical-ward-at-Churachandpur-hospital-II-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-658425%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20diversity%20within%20the%20SEAR%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20every%20country%20has%20a%20health%20problem%20unique%20to%20its%20own.%20How%20can%20you%20bring%20synergy%20amidst%20all%20of%20this%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20there%20exists%20a%20lot%20of%20diversity%20but%20the%20principles%20like%20universal%20health%20coverage%20are%20the%20same.%20So%2C%20while%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20intend%20to%20implement%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20formula%20and%20stress%20for%20a%20tailored%20approach%20for%20each%20country%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20that%20these%20countries%20can%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20depending%20on%20their%20specific%20challenges.%20For%20example%2C%20NCDs%20for%20India%2C%20climate%20change%20for%20Maldives%2C%20migration%20for%20Japan%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20SEAR%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20decades%2C%20would%20be%20home%20to%20the%20most%20ageing%20populations.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20going%20to%20create%20a%20challenge%20in%20terms%20of%20access%20to%20health%2C%20again%2C%20but%20also%2C%20otherwise.%20What%20is%20your%20prescription%20to%20deal%20with%20that%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20very%20important%20question.%20Japan%20and%20Singapore%20are%20good%20examples%20to%20learn%20from%2C%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20firstly%2C%20we%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20ageing%20is%20recognised%20and%20acknowledged%20as%20part%20of%20our%20health%20policymaking.%20Primary%20healthcare%20has%20to%20be%20strengthened%20for%20the%20elderly.%20Besides%20physical%20care%2C%20programmes%20for%20their%20%5Bageing%20population%E2%80%99s%5D%20psychological%20and%20emotional%20care%20have%20to%20be%20incorporated%20as%20part%20of%20the%20programmes%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20elderly%20age%20in%20a%20healthy%20manner%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20the%20burden%20of%20NCDs%20is%20already%20high%2C%20we%20have%20to%20provide%20them%20an%20active%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20opportunities%20to%20work%2C%20if%20they%20are%20interested%2C%20even%20when%20they%20are%20not%20a%20part%20of%20workforce%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELastly%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20about%20a%20challenge%20that%20is%20somewhat%20unique%20to%20India%2C%20which%20is%20unbridled%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20the%20unscientific%20use%20of%20various%20alternative%20systems%20of%20medicine%20products.%20How%20big%20a%20problem%20is%20this%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETraditional%20medicine%20is%20important%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20based%20on%20very%20good%2C%20proven%2C%20and%20scientifically%20robust%20research%20with%20good%20evidence%2C%20definitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAre%20the%20governments%20doing%20enough%20to%20implement%20in%20practice%20what%20you%20just%20said%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20to%20be%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20legislation%20in%20place%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20right%20and%20constant%20messaging%20%E2%80%93%20that%20anything%20%5Ba%20drug%20or%20a%20supplement%5D%20has%20to%20be%20consumed%20only%20if%20it%20passes%20the%20scientific%20muster.%20Mass%20awareness%20programmes%20are%20urgently%20needed%20for%20this%2C%20and%20the%20youth%20has%20to%20be%20engaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everything%20can%20be%20done%20by%20the%20governments.%20If%20there%20is%20evidence%20saying%20something%20is%20not%20good%20to%20be%20consumed%20and%20if%20one%20is%20still%20hell-bent%20on%20doing%20that%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20problem.%20%5BIt%E2%80%99s%5D%20a%20challenge%20in%20terms%20of%20behavioural%20science%2C%20dealing%20with%20which%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20engagement%20with%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698766190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31201048%2Fimage-1466.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fconfident-victory-public-health-experience-shambhu-acharya-who-sear-office%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20The%20Wire%2C%20Shambhu%20Acharya%20answers%20several%20questions%20ranging%20from%20Ayushman%C2%A0Bharat%2C%20health%20financing%20models%2C%20and%20WHO's%20engagement%20with%20governments%20in%20the%20Southeast%20Asia%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fconfident-victory-public-health-experience-shambhu-acharya-who-sear-office%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Police%20Commandos%2C%20Sent%20As%20Reinforcements%20After%20Cop%20Was%20Shot%2C%20Ambushed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20Manipur%20Police%20commandos%20sent%20to%20a%20border%20town%20as%20reinforcements%20after%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20was%20shot%20dead%20this%20morning%20were%20ambushed%20by%20suspected%20insurgents%20on%20their%20way%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20Many%20commandos%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20ambush%20that%20happened%2010%20km%20short%20of%20Tengnoupal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETroops%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20rushed%20to%20the%20ambush%20site%20and%20rescued%20the%20police%20commandos%2C%20government%20sources%20said.%20Many%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKuki%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20in%20statements%20alleged%20it%20was%20a%20retaliatory%20shoot-out%20with%20Kuki%20village%20voluntee