n%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104862455.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChoreographer%20Vaibhavi%20Merchant%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Salman%20Khan's%20Tiger%203%2C%20recently%20opened%20up%20about%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20prep%20for%20Not%20Ramaiya%20Vastavaiya%20song%20from%20his%20all-time%20blockbuster%20Jawan%2C%20directed%20by%20Atlee.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvaibhavi-merchant-reveals-shah-rukh-khan-went-out-of-his-way-for-doing-not-ramaiya-vastavaiya-song-from-jawan-he-would-sweat-a-lot-on-an-ac-set%2Farticleshow%2F104862455.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20Helps%20Resolve%20Custody%20Dispute%20In%202%20Weeks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20intervention%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20has%20ensured%20an%20amicable%20settlement%20of%20a%20child%20custody%20dispute%20in%20just%20a%20fortnight.%20Showing%20his%20humane%20side%2C%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20asked%20the%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20the%20child%20and%2C%20during%20the%20final%20hearing%2C%20also%20asked%20the%20eight-year-old%20-%20in%20Hindi%20-%20how%20he%20was%20doing%20in%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20child%20(all%20names%20are%20being%20withheld%20to%20protect%20their%20privacy)%20got%20married%20in%202014%20and%20trouble%20began%20in%20their%20marriage%20a%20year%20later.%20According%20to%20the%20woman's%20petition%2C%20their%20son%20was%20born%20in%20July%202015%20and%2C%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20later%2C%20she%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20her%20matrimonial%20home%20because%20her%20husband%20had%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20their%20family%20members%20said%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20support%20her%20and%20the%20infant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20the%20husband%20sent%20her%20a%20divorce%20notice%20in%202021.%20With%20the%20divorce%20pending%2C%20he%20went%20to%20meet%20the%20child%20and%20took%20him%20away%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20promising%20to%20return%20him%20to%20his%20mother%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20June%2026.%20When%20he%20failed%20to%20do%20that%20and%20did%20not%20answer%20her%20calls%2C%20the%20mother%20went%20to%20Dehradun%20to%20meet%20the%20boy%2C%20only%20to%20find%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20his%20family%20had%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20to%20Delhi%20and%2C%20when%20she%20could%20not%20find%20the%20family%2C%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20asking%20for%20the%20child%20to%20be%20produced.%20When%20the%20hearings%20began%2C%20she%20found%20out%20that%20the%20boy%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20Dehradun%20again%2C%20outside%20the%20court's%20jurisdiction.%20She%20finally%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20asked%20for%20him%20to%20be%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgreement%20Reached%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20hearing%20of%20the%20case%20on%20October%2017%2C%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20heard%20the%20mother's%20side.%20Keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20an%20eight-year-old's%20future%20was%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20asked%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20the%20child%20and%20see%20if%20the%20matter%20could%20be%20resolved%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20Monday%2C%20Ms%20Bhati%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20she%20had%20called%20them%20to%20her%20house%20and%20spoken%20to%20them%20and%20they%20had%20all%20agreed%20that%20the%20child%20would%20stay%20with%20the%20mother%20for%20two%20years%20and%20the%20parents%20would%20take%20a%20mutual%20decision%20on%20what%20comes%20next%20after%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20Ms%20Bhati%20said%20that%20the%20child%20seemed%20very%20intelligent%20and%20this%20prompted%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20to%20turn%20to%20him%20and%20ask%20in%20Hindi%20how%20he%20was%20doing%20in%20school.%20The%20child%20replied%20that%20he%20hadn't%20been%20attending%20school%20because%20it%20was%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20he%20had%20been%20travelling%20with%20his%20father.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExpressing%20satisfaction%20with%20the%20agreement%2C%20the%20bench%20closed%20the%20matter%20and%20also%20granted%20a%20divorce%20to%20the%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698765120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4s1m01fo_cji-dy-chandrachud-ani_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-helps-resolve-custody-dispute-in-2-weeks-4532655%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20intervention%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20has%20ensured%20an%20amicable%20settlement%20of%20a%20child%20custody%20dispute%20in%20less%20than%20a%20fortnight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-helps-resolve-custody-dispute-in-2-weeks-4532655%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-helps-resolve-custody-dispute-in-2-weeks-4532655%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-helps-resolve-custody-dispute-in-2-weeks-4532655%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden's%20Arab%20American%20support%20drops%20amid%20Gaza%20conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698764828000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104862521%2Cimgsize-1548044.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h