ts%20for%20the%20job%2C%20despite%20their%20repeated%20requests%20to%20receive%20the%20agreed-upon%20amount%20in%20full.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20summer%2C%20the%20two%20firms%20then%20agreed%20to%20settle%2C%20with%20JMF%20paying%20its%20subcontractor%20%2423%2C500.%20However%2C%20in%20August%2C%20the%20welding%20company%20sent%20a%20flatbed%20truck%20loaded%20with%20a%20specially%20constructed%20box%20jammed%20with%20coins%20that%20weighed%20nearly%206%2C500%20pounds.%20The%20box%20was%20filled%20with%20loose%20quarters%2C%20nickels%2C%20and%20pennies%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdavid-kirke-the-man-who-performed-worlds-first-bungee-jump-dies-at-78-4531716%5C%22%3EDavid%20Kirke%2C%20The%20Man%20Who%20Performed%20World's%20First%20Bungee%20Jump%2C%20Dies%20At%2078%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFired%20Up%20Fabrication's%20attorney%2C%20Danielle%20Beem%20called%20this%20stunt%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20and%20grand%20waste%20of%20time%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20the%20coin%20delivery%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbolic%20middle%20finger%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Beem%20also%20called%20the%20attempted%20coin%20delivery%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20F-U%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJMF's%20lawyers%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20coins%20%26quot%3Bconstituted%20a%20tender%20of%20the%20settlement%20funds%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20JMF%20has%20complied%20with%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement.%20The%20settlement%20agreement%20did%20not%20outline%20any%20specific%20form%20for%20the%20payment%26quot%3B.%20Lawyers%20for%20the%20company%20also%20added%20that%20they%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20harassing%20the%20subcontractor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Judge%20Findley%20appeared%20to%20agree%20with%20Fired%20Up%20Frabrication's%20lawyers.%20He%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20apparently%20ob