99s%20column%20on%20the%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20piece%20is%20as%20much%20a%20celebration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(so%20far)%20invincible%20World%20Cup%20cricket%20team%2C%20as%20it%20is%20of%20its%20diversity.%20Never%20has%20an%20Indian%20team%20in%20my%20living%20memory%20or%20beyond%20that%2C%20been%20so%20representative%20of%20what%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20is.%20Unity%20in%20diversity%20may%20sound%20a%20trite%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20are%20living%20in%20divisive%20times%2C%20but%20it%20still%20best%20sums%20up%20a%20country%20which%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20different%20religions%20and%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20may%20be%20screaming%20%E2%80%98Rohit%2C%20Rohit%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Kohli%2C%20Kohli%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20lethal%20bowling%20and%20the%20variety%20it%20has%20to%20offer%20that%20is%20leading%20India%E2%80%99s%20unstoppable%20march%20and%20makes%20them%20easily%20the%20most%20favoured%20team%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20323px)%2085vw%2C%20323px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22323%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%20976w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-244x300.jpg%20244w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-833x1024.jpg%20833w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22397%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20warriors%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Ramgarhia%20Sikh%2C%20two%20Muslims%2C%20one%20from%20an%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20community%20and%20an%20upper%20caste%20person%20%E2%80%93%20are%20sending%20fear%20down%20the%20spine%20of%20the%20batsmen.%20They%20are%2C%20through%20their%20sheer%20skill%20and%20self-belief%2C%20entertaining%20thousands%20inside%20the%20stadium.%20The%20thunderous%2C%20cacophonic%20sounds%20that%20create%20a%20wave%20of%20support%20for%20the%20home%20team%20must%20sound%20like%20a%20death%20knell%20to%20the%20opposition%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20united%20flavour%20of%20Indian%20national%20identities%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Kuldip%20Yadav%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20make%20an%20impregnable%20shield%2C%20and%2C%20probably%2C%20hold%20a%20lesson%20for%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20something%20very%20strange%20and%20even%20intriguing%20about%20our%20nation%2C%20where%20caste%20and%20religion%20are%20the%20two%20most%20important%20markers%20of%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20yet%20we%20are%20shy%20to%20acknowledge%20it%20publicly.%20Those%20who%20control%20the%20levers%20of%20power%20would%20like%20us%20to%20believe%20caste%20does%20not%20matter%20but%20are%20proud%20of%20their%20upper%20caste%20lineage.%20Cricket%2C%20unlike%20many%20sports%20in%20India%2C%20has%20for%20long%20remained%20a%20preserve%20of%20the%20ruling%20elites.%20Most%20cricketers%20of%20the%20past%20may%20not%20have%20come%20from%20rich%20backgrounds%2C%20but%20were%20mostly%20city-bred%20middle-class%20Brahmins.%20Sure%2C%20Muslims%20and%20a%20few%20Sikhs%20or%20an%20odd%20Christian%20did%20break%20into%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20but%20by%20and%20large%2C%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20struggle%20to%20find%20lower%20caste%20representation%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%2080s%E2%80%99%20cricketing%20revolution%2C%20symbolised%20by%20India%20winning%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20dynamic%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20a%20change%20started%20taking%20place.%20Kapil%20himself%20was%20from%20a%20non-cricketing%20centre%20like%20Chandigarh.%20When%20he%20lifted%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Lord%E2%80%99s%20balcony%2C%20Kapil%20ignited%20a%20billion%20dreams.%20For%20young%20kids%20in%20the%20lanes%20and%20bylanes%20of%20cities%20or%20village%20%3Cem%3Emaidans%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20fantasy%20to%20aspire%20to%20play%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20late%2090s%20and%20finally%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20boys%20from%20small%20towns%20were%20finding%20a%20place%20in%20the%20team%3A%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20being%20its%20best%20example%20and%20his%202011%20World%20Cup%20winning%20six%2C%20played%20with%20imperious%20nonchalance%2C%20remains%20an%20image%20no%20Indian%20can%20forget.%20This%20mix%20of%20big-city%20boys%20and%20small-town%20aspirants%2C%20backed%20by%20an%20expanding%20base%20and%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20game%2C%20has%20today%20propelled%20India%20to%20the%20number%20one%20team%20position%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diversity%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20is%20obviously%20spreading%20and%20today%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20no%20longer%20finds%20itself%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20religious%2Fcaste%20social%20matrix.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20would%20not%20be%20overstating%20the%20fact%20that%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20a%20phenomenal%20bowler%2C%20whose%20unusual%20skills%20and%20intuitive%20understanding%20of%20his%20craft%20make%20him%20almost%20unplayable%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20who%20follows%20the%20more%20conventional%20path.%20With%20the%20swerving%20ball%2C%20released%20after%20great%20dexterity%20from%20his%20cocked%20wrists%2C%20he%20creates%20magic%20to%20rattle%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Siraj%2C%20the%20least%20experienced%20of%20the%20trio%20but%20never%20short%20of%20effort%20and%20enthusiasm%2C%20keeps%20surprising%20the%20batsmen%20with%20his%20pace%20and%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20these%20three%20were%20not%20a%20handful%2C%20the%20batsmen%20now%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20different%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20foxy%2C%20wily%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20aided%20by%20steely%20wrists%2C%20spins%20the%20ball%20both%20ways.%20His%20control%20of%20the%20pace%2C%20impeccable%20line%20and%20length%20leave%20the%20batsmen%20bewildered.%20Should%20he%20go%20forward%20or%20back%3F%20Will%20the%20ball%20turn%20away%2C%20come%20in%20or%20straighten%3F%20He%20is%20doomed%20in%20this%20web%20of%20confusion%20and%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20is%20exceptional.%20He%20is%20like%20a%20locomotive%20machine%2C%20which%20requires%20no%20greasing%20and%20can%20deliver%20ball%20after%20ball%20with%20variations%2C%20just%20minimum%20enough%20to%20fox%20the%20batsman.%20His%20control%20over%20his%20length%2C%20his%20athleticism%20and%20calm%20in%20nerve-wracking%20situations%20make%20him%20simply%20an%20indispensable%20member%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20vital%20cog%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20diversity%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20team%3A%20a%20Dalit.%20What%20does%20it%20speak%20of%20a%20nation%20when%20a%20community%20that%20constitutes%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20population%20has%20no%20representation%20in%20its%20most%20popular%20sport%3F%20If%20even%20today%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20decades%20back%20and%20cite%20Palwankar%20Baloo%20as%20an%20example%20of%20a%20Dalit%20having%20played%20for%20India%2C%20it%20goes%20to%20show%20that%20we%20have%20failed%20the%20community.%20There%20is%20not%20enough%20space%2C%20access%20and%20encouragement%20to%20break%20through%20a%20systemic%20malaise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20for%20now%20celebrate%20the%20progress%20that%20has%20been%20made%20and%20hope%20that%20there%20is%20more%20in%20the%20future.%20As%20India%20inches%20closer%20towards%20its%20goal%20of%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Indian%20fans