t%20and%20what%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Magic%20Bus%20appointed%20Bittu%20as%20one%20of%20their%20community%20coordinators.%20While%20her%20ambition%20is%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20she%20also%20plans%20to%20play%20kabaddi%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20can.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20give%20me%20full%20support.%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98When%20my%20daughter%20is%20on%20the%20right%20track%2C%20why%20would%20I%20stop%20her%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Matthew%2C%20these%20stories%20motivate%20him%20further.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20emotional%20aspect%20of%20our%20work%20reminds%20me%20of%20our%20mission%E2%80%99s%20importance%20and%20the%20need%20to%20stay%20rooted%20in%20the%20communities%20we%20serve.%20By%20understanding%20their%20struggles%20and%20empathising%20with%20their%20challenges%2C%20we%20ensure%20our%20programmes%20remain%20relevant%20and%20effective.%20This%20powerful%20motivation%20drives%20our%20commitment%20to%20doing%20right%20by%20them%20and%20striving%20for%20continuous%20improvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20contributed%20by%20the%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698761468000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20sports%20to%20teach%20crucial%20life%20skills%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20Foundation%20India%20is%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20impacting%204%2C00%2C000%20adolescent%20girls%20in%2022%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GE%20T%26amp%3BD%20India%20wins%20Rs%20500%20crore%20orders%20from%20Power%20Grid%20Corpora