%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20live%20a%20green%20life.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20free%20from%20the%20rat%20race%20and%20lead%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20individuals%20prefer%20eco-friendly%20homes%20to%20lower%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20minimise%20energy%20usage%2C%20cut%20long-term%20costs%2C%20reduce%20waste%2C%20and%20promote%20healthier%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20can%20construct%20an%20eco-friendly%20home%20by%20first%20understanding%20the%20qualities%20of%20the%20scrap%20material%20used%20for%20construction%2C%20engaging%20in%20collaborative%20brainstorming%20sessions%20with%20skilled%20tradesmen%2C%20and%20cultivating%20a%20diverse%20capacity%20for%20design%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20also%20shares%20that%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20register%20their%20container%20home%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20ACs%20or%20coolers%20to%20regulate%20temperature%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2071-1050%2F14%2F21%2F14393%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESustainability%20Considerations%20of%20Green%20Buildings%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%202022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20mentions%20that%20sustainable%20buildings%20can%20conserve%2040%20percent%20more%20energy%20compared%20with%20traditional%20buildings%2C%20increasing%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20decreasing%20carbon%20emissions.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20low-carbon%20materials%20in%20green%20buildings%20reduce%20lifecycle%20emissions%20of%20buildings%20by%20up%20to%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20conserve%20energy%20in%20their%20unique%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244161%2Fthese-10-eco-friendly-homes-will-inspire-you-to-live-sustainably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20father-son%20pair%20have%20employed%20an%20innovative%20masonry%20technique%2C%C2%A0the%20%E2%80%98Rat%20Trap%20Bond%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20popularised%20by%20renowned%20architect%20Laurie%20Baker%20for%20passive%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traditional%20methods%2C%20this%20technique%20involves%20placing%20the%20bricks%20vertically%20rather%20than%20horizontally%2C%20aiding%20in%20temperature%20regulation%20and%20energy%20conservation%20within%20the%20structure.%20It%20creates%20a%20cavity%20in%20the%20walls%20and%20allows%20the%20thickness%20to%20remain%20the%20same%20as%20a%20conventional%20brick%20masonry%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cavity%20helps%20cut%20down%20the%20number%20of%20bricks%20and%20mortar%20used%20by%20up%20to%2030%20percent.%20This%20further%20reduces%20carbon%20footprints%20and%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramachandrudu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20container%20house%20boasts%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20drawing%20room%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20staircase.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333374%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20container%20house%20boasts%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20drawing%20room%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20staircase.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20a%20treat%20for%20the%20eyes%2C%20the%20walls%20promote%20natural%20light%20and%20ventilation%20in%20the%20house%20as%20cavities%20act%20as%20thermal%20insulators%20providing%20warmth%20in%20winter%20and%20cool%20air%20in%20summer.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20have%20ACs%20or%20air%20coolers.%20During%20summers%2C%20usually%2C%20the%20interior%20temperature%20is%20at%20least%20seven%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20repurposed%20old%20wood%20for%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20buying%20new%20wooden%20furniture%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20opted%20to%20source%20antique%20wooden%20doors%2C%20planks%2C%20and%20staircases%20from%20demolished%20homes%20within%20the%20city.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20repurposed%20old%20glass%20doors%20from%20restaurant%20refrigerators%20to%20craft%20elegant%20glass%20window%20doors.%20Furthermore%2C%20they%20used%20cycle%20rims%20to%20create%20unique%20window%20frames%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20and%20resourcefulness%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20construction%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reused%20two%20truckloads%20of%20old%20wood%20in%20the%20construction.%20The%20old%20wood%20gives%20a%20typical%20old%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%20to%20our%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20harvest%20sunlight%20and%20rain%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20installed%20an%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269780%2Fmy-zero-waste-home-saves-70-energy-by-using-the-sun-to-run-appliances%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20capacity%20of%20one%20kilowatt%20to%20fulfil%20the%20household%E2%80%99s%20essential%20energy%20requirements.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20family%20has%20successfully%20reduced%20their%20monthly%20electricity%20bill%20from%20Rs%20800%20to%20a%20mere%20Rs%2080.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20annually%20collects%2040%2C000%20litres%20of%20rainwater%20and%20redirects%20an%20excess%20of%20three%20lakh%20litres%20to%20recharge%20the%20borewell.%20After%20filtering%20water%20through%20sand%20filters%2C%20the%20family%20ensures%20the%20water%E2%80%99s%20purity%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20use%20it%20for%20drinking%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharani%20has%20also%20made%20unique%20bricks%20from%20styrofoam%20by%20mixed%20it%20with%20cement.%20Close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333372%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBharani%20has%20also%20made%20unique%20bricks%20from%20styrofoam%20by%20mixing%20it%20with%20cement.%20Close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20make%20our%20own%20chemical-free%20home%20products%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20has%20implemented%20a%20greywater%20treatment%20system%2C%20which%20effectively%20repurposes%20treated%20greywater%20from%20kitchen%20sinks%2C%20basins%2C%20and%20bathrooms%20for%20watering%20the%20plants%20in%20their%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20encountered%20a%20foul%20smell%20coming%20from%20nearby%20tanks%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20accumulated%20dirty%20water.%20We%20realised%20that%20the%20smell%20was%20mostly%20because%20of%20the%20various%20oils%20and%20chemical%20detergents%20we%20used%2C%20which%20polluted%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20this%20set%20them%20to%20start%20another%20exciting%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20chemical%20cleaners%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20started%20making%20natural%20cleaners%20using%20a%20blend%20of%20bio%20enzymes%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20and%20wood%20ash.%20To%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebio%20enzymes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20collects%20flowers%20and%20lime%20waste%2C%20adding%20natural%20ingredients%20such%20as%20fenugreek%2C%20coconut%2C%20rice%2C%20aloe%20vera%2C%20black%20seeds%2C%20and%20hibiscus.%20These%20elements%20are%20combined%20to%20make%20powerful%20shampoos%2C%20body%20washes%20and%20liquid%20cleaners%20for%20w