0in%20curbing%20employees'%20rights%20to%20switch%20employers%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20construed%20as%20potentially%20a%20contravention%20of%20competition%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20regret%20that%20you%20interpreted%20my%20courtesy%20of%20taking%20your%20call%20and%20listening%20to%20your%20request%20as%20assent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Pilots%20has%20described%20the%20alleged%20mass%20resignations%20from%20Akasa%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bindication%26quot%3B%20of%20employee%20discontent%2C%20while%20India's%20aviation%20watchdog%20has%20said%20it%20cannot%20interfere%20in%20matters%20related%20to%20employment%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20newest%20airline%2C%20Akasa%20started%20flying%20in%202022%2C%20garnering%20a%20market%20share%20of%204%25.%20It%20competes%20with%20IndiGo%2C%20which%20commands%20a%20share%20of%2060%25%20and%20Tata%20Group's%20airlines%20that%20together%20have%20a%20share%20of%2025.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Sept%2021%20letter%2C%20Air%20India's%20Wilson%20expressed%20the%20hope%20that%20Akasa%20would%20make%20investments%20to%20%26quot%3Battract%2C%20retain%20and%20develop%26quot%3B%20its%20own%20staff%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20airline%20looked%20forward%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontinuing%20healthy%20competition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698759900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fi0e7t5sc_campbell-wilson-vinay-dubey_625x300_31_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcampbell-wilson-vinay-dube-air-india-akasa-ceos-exchange-barbs-over-poaching-of-pilots-report-4530752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20executives%20of%20Air%20India%20and%20Akasa%20Air%20have%20privately%20exchanged%20barbs%20over%20the%20poaching%20of%20pilots%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20accusing%20its%20bigger%20rival%20of%20rule%20violations%2C%20provoking%20a%20reply%20that%20collusion%20to%20curb%20job%20switching%20can%20breach%20competition%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcampbell-wilson-vinay-dube-air-india-akasa-ceos-exchange-barbs-over-poaching-of-pilots-report-4530752%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcampbell-wilson-vinay-dube-air-india-akasa-ceos-exchange-barbs-over-poaching-of-pilots-report-4530752%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcampbell-wilson-vinay-dube-air-india-akasa-ceos-exchange-barbs-over-poaching-of-pilots-report-4530752%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Major%20'White%20Hydrogen'%20Deposit%20Found%20In%20France.%20How%20It%20Could%20Save%20The%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20scientists%20in%20France%20recently%20discovered%20what%20may%20be%20the%20largest%20known%20deposit%20of%20a%20clean%20energy%20resource%20that%20could%20revolutionize%20our%20world%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F29%2Fclimate%2Fwhite-hydrogen-fossil-fuels-climate%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0Scientists%20Jacques%20Pironon%20and%20Phillipe%20De%20Donato%2C%20who%20were%20actually%C2%A0looking%20for%20fossil%20fuels%20beneath%20the%20ground%20of%20northeastern%20France%2C%20accidentally%20discovered%20a%20significant%20deposit%20of%20white%20hydrogen.%20They%20found%20a%2020%25%20higher%20concentration%20of%20hydrogen%20at%201%2C250%20meters%20below%20the%20ground%20and%20estimated%20that%20the%20deposit%20could%20contain%20between%206%20million%20and%20250%20million%20metric%20tons%EF%BB%BF%20of%20hydrogen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20white%20hydrogen%20is%20naturally%20produced%20in%20the%20Earth's%20crust%20and%20is%20considered%20a%20potential%20clean%20energy.%C2%A0Unlike%20other%20forms%20of%20hydrogen%2C%20white%20hydrogen%20only%20produces%20water%20when%20it%20is%20burned%2C%20making%20it%20an%20exceptionally%20clean%20energy%20source%20with%20enormous%20potential.%20It%C2%A0%20has%20been%20named%20'white'%20since%20the%20%26quot%3Bproduction%20doesn't%20generate%20greenhouse%20gases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20hydrogen%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20cleaner%20alternative%20in%20various%20applications%2C%20such%20as%20fuel%20cells%20for%20vehicles%20or%20industrial%20processes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20is%20all%20the%20more%20significant%20because%C2%A0scientists%20thought%20mass%20amounts%20could%20only%20be%20produced%20in%20a%20laboratory.%C2%A0Other%20forms%20of%20the%20gas%20like%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20gray%20hydrogen%20are%20produced%20in%20the%20lab%20through%20electrolysis.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20price%20of%20this%20gas%20will%20be%20cheaper%20and%20it%20can%20be%20a%20replacement%20for%20conventional%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''If%20you%20had%20asked%20me%20four%20years%20ago%20what%20I%20thought%20about%20natural%20hydrogen%2C%20I%20would%20have%20told%20you%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20it%20doesn't%20exist.%20Hydrogen's%20out%20there%2C%20we%20know%20it's%20around%2C''%20said%20Geoffrey%20Ellis%2C%20a%20geochemist%20with%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeochemist%20Viacheslav%20Zgonnik%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20it%20could%20help%20us%20%26quot%3Bget%20to%20speed%26quot%3B%20on%20saving%20the%20world%20from%20the%20climate%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20hydrogen%20deposits%20have%20also%20been%20discovered%20in%20places%20like%20Russia%2C%20Oman%2C%20France%2C%20Mali%2C%20and%20others.%20Experts%20estimate%20globally%20there%20could%20be%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20tons%20of%20white%20hydrogen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclo8r0k0q000t2e68htm0gxcb%40published%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E''Most%20of%20this%20is%20almost%20certainly%20going%20to%20be%20in%20very%20small%20accumulations%20or%20very%20far%20offshore%2C%20or%20just%20too%20deep%20to%20actually%20be%20economic%20to%20produce.%20But%20if%20just%201%25%20can%20be%20found%20and%20produced%2C%20it%20would%20provide%20500%20million%20tons%20of%20hydrogen%20for%20200%20years%2C''%20Mr%20Ellis%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclo8r0k0q000t2e68htm0gxcb%40published%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3ESeveral%20start-ups%20are%20already%20exploring%20how%20to%20commercialize%20white%20hydrogen.%20However%2C%20the%20development%20of%20the%20resource%20might%20take%20around%20200%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclo8r0k0q000t2e68htm0gxcb%40published%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20other%20issues%20like%20regulatory%20barriers%20and%20production%20costs.%20The%20estimated%20production%20cost%20of%20white%20hydrogen%20is%20currently%20around%20%241%20per%20kilogram%2C%20compared%20to%20%246%20per%20kilogram%20for%20green%20hydrogen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698759900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fsk6okgbo_scientists-istockphoto-large_625x300_21_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fmajor-white-hydrogen-deposit-found-in-france-heres-how-it-could-revolutionise-the-world-4532198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22White%20hydrog