m%20vulnerability.%20Will%20wait%20till%20they%20give%20a%20report.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20did%2C%20however%2C%20stress%20that%20the%20government%20is%20still%20working%20on%20moving%20large%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%20including%20legacy%20data%20collected%20over%20the%20past%20decades%2C%20to%20safe%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20government%20ecosystem%2C%20there%20is%20data%20from%20the%20centre%20and%20states%2C%20and%20ministries%20and%20departments.%20Lot%20of%20data...%20including%20legacy%20data%20that%20peaked%20during%20COVID-19.%20It%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20transition%2C%20in%20an%20orderly%20and%20non-disruptive%20manner%20to%20being%20a%20responsible%20keeper%20of%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-apple-must-say-if-devices-secure-says-minister-on-hacking-row-4531544%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20%26quot%3BApple%20Must%20Say%20If%20Devices%20Secure%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Minister%20On%20'Hacking'%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20have%20to%20recognise%20the%20government%20ecosystem%20will%20take%20a%20little%20longer%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20bullet%20proof%20set-up...%20one%20which%20manages%20data%20and%20keeps%20it%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20responsible%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekhar%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20wasn't%20just%20government%20data%20that%20had%20to%20be%20secured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20applies%20to%20MSMEs%20and%20other%20small%20businesses%2C%20which%20are%20custodians%20of%20consumer%20data.%20It%20will%20take%20time%20for%20all%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20new%20framework%2C%20in%20which%20there%20is%20more%20responsibility%20and%20accountability%20about%20how%20different%20individuals%20and%20entities%20collect%2C%20store%20and%20access%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%20Resecurity%2C%20a%20United%20States-based%20global%20cybersecurity%20solutions%20provider%2C%20published%20a%20report%20claiming%20%26quot%3Bmillions%20of%20personally%20identifiable%20information%20(PII)%20records%2C%20including%20Aadhaar%20cards%2C%20belonging%20to%20Indian%20residents%2C%20(are)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.resecurity.com%2Fblog%2Farticle%2Fpii-belonging-to-indian-citizens-including-their-aadhaar-ids-offered-for-sale-on-the-dark-web%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20offered%20for%20sale%20on%20the%20Dark%20Web%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blog%20post%20published%20on%20October%2015%2C%20Resecurity%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20actor%26quot%3B%20(identified%20as%20'pwn0001')%20was%20brokering%20access%20to%20these%20records%2C%20and%20that%20these%20were%20available%20for%20sale%20for%20%2480%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20allegedly%20on%20sale%20also%20included%20age%2C%20gender%20and%20addresses%20of%20millions%20of%20Indian%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20post%20also%20claimed%20a%20leak%20from%20August%20-%20brokered%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20actor%26quot%3B%20called%20'Lucius'%20-%20offered%201.8TB%20of%20data%20%26quot%3Bimpacting%20an%20unnamed%20India%20internal%20law%20enforcement%20organization%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20at%20least%20three%20instances%20of%20large-scale%20Aadhaar%20leaks%20last%20year%2C%20including%20one%20in%20which%20farmers'%20data%20stored%20on%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20website%2C%20were%20reportedly%20made%20available%20on%20the%20dark%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698759420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fke18j5s_rajeev-chandrasekhar-650_650x400_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faadhaar-data-breach-rajeev-chandrasekhar-not-happy-probe-on-minister-on-alleged-leak-of-indians-private-data-4532266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20is%20investigating%20reports%20that%20confidential%20data%20of%20over%2080%20crore%20Indians%2C%20including%20names%20and%20phone%2C%20passport%20and%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20were%20leaked%20on%20the%20dark%20web%2C%20junior%20IT%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faadhaar-data-breach-rajeev-chandrasekhar-not-happy-probe-on-minister-on-alleged-leak-of-indians-private-data-4532266%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faadhaar-data-breach-rajeev-chandrasekhar-not-happy-probe-on-minister-on-alleged-leak-of-indians-private-data-4532266%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faadhaar-data-breach-rajeev-chandrasekhar-not-happy-probe-on-minister-on-alleged-leak-of-indians-private-data-4532266%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Hindutva%20Politics%20and%20the%20Belief%20in%20'Evil%20Eye'%20Have%20in%20Common%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31184258%2Fevil-eye.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP-led%20NDA%20and%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20of%20INDIA%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%20One%20of%20the%20important%20factors%20both%20alliances%20will%20emphasise%20is%20economic%20growth.%20Even%20though%20NDA-I%20was%20considered%20by%20many%20to%20be%20a%20failure%20on%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20NDA-II%20won%20with%20an%20even%20greater%20majority%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20economic%20performance%20is%20still%20relevant%20for%20voting%20choices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20continues%20to%20win%20elections%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20despite%20economic%20mishaps%2C%20one%20must%20concede%20that%20there%20is%20more%20than%20meets%20the%20eye.%20Several%20arguments%20have%20been%20presented%20by%20scholars%20to%20decipher%20religious%2C%20caste%20and%20cultural%20angles%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20to%20garner%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20help%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CGodi%20Media%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20dedicated%20IT%20team%2C%20blended%20with%20the%20model%20of%20crony%20capitalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20is%20one%20aspect%20that%20has%20been%20ignored%3A%20the%20day-to-day%20culture%20of%20the%20masses%20that%20enables%20political%20ideologies%20such%20as%20the%20Sangh%3Ci%3E%20parivar%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20thrive%20and%20reap%20benefits.%20In%20India%2C%20this%20culture%20includes%20a%20strong%20belief%20in%20hierarchy%2C%20inequality%2C%20gender%20difference%2C%20notions%20of%20purity%20and%20pollution%2C%20stereotypes%20about%20%E2%80%98others%E2%80%99%20and%20unscientific%20beliefs%20such%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fculture%2Farticle%2F20180216-the-strange-power-of-the-evil-eye%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eevil%20eye%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20black%20magic.%20They%20are%20a%20normalised%20part%20of%20culture%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20continuation%20of%20these%20belief%20systems%20and%20practices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESpeaking%20the%20political%20language%20of%20the%20masses%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20Congress%20party%20protested%20against%20the%20rising%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20in%20India%20by%20wearing%20black%20clothes%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20rebuked%20them%20by%20saying%20that%20people%20would%20not%20fall%20for%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fthose-believing-in-black-magic-wont-earn-peoples-trust-pm-modi-taunts-oppn-8082900%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98black%20magic%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98.%3Cspan%3E%20This%20is%20not%20merely%20an%20analogy%20but%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20deep-rooted%20social%20beliefs%20of%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%E2%80%99s%20annual%20Crimes%20in%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ereports%20showed%20that%20between%202014-2021%2C%20819%20murders%20were%20committed%20where%20the%20victims%20were%20accused%20of%20witchcraft.%20These%20are%20only%20reported%20cases%2C%20so%20the%20actual%20number%20may%20be%20higher.%20Most%20often%2C%20the%20victims%20of%20this%20violence%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fwitch-hunts-today-abuse-of-women-superstition-and-murder-collide-in-india%2F%5C%22%3Ewomen%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20people%20from%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trio%20of%20jealousy%2C%20evil%20eye%20and%20black%20magic%20has%20to%20be%20understood%20in%20tandem%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20this%20particular%20aspect%20of%20the%20belief%20system.%20Jealousy%20is%20mild%20and%20common%20and%20often%20individualistic%20or%20personal.%20It%20is%20accepted%20that%20people%20are%20generally%20jealous%20of%20each%20other.%20However%2C%20women%20are%20stereotyped%20as%20being%20more%20jealous%20than%20men.%20It%20is%20a%20common%20belief%20that%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20relatives%20and%20neighbours%20will%20be%20jealous%20if%20one%20does%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExtreme%20jealousy%20leads%20to%20the%20belief%20in%20an%20evil%20eye%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20at%20times%20involuntary%20and%20at%20other%20times%20a%20deliberate%20act.%20The%20evil%20eye%20can%20also%20cause%20disturbances%20to%20others%20and%20is%20considered%20dangerous.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ultimate%20stage%20of%20jealousy%20is%20black%20magic%2C%20a%20voluntary%20action%20intending%20to%20cause%20damage%20to%20others.%20Apart%20from%20jealousy%20and%20black%20magic%2C%20the%20evil%20eye%20is%20so%20common%20in%20our%20practices%20it%20looks%20like%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20escape%20from%20this%20belief%20system%20and%20determines%20our%20daily%20actions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEvil%20eye%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvil%20eye%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3EDrishti%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3ENara%20Drishti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20a%20belief%20that%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20jealousy-induced%20gaze%20or%20bad%20intentions%20could%20bring%20misfortune.%20If%20one%20is%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20evil%20eye%2C%20a%20person%20(mostly%20children)%20may%20get%20a%20stomach%20ache%20or%20indigestion%3B%20a%20newly%20married%20couple%20may%20quarrel%3B%20and%20the%20beautiful%20bride%20may%20get%20a%20headache.%20People%20in%20a%20beautiful%20house%20might%20face%20problems.%20A%20business%20may%20not%20prosper.%20A%20for-hire%20vehicle%20might%20not%20find%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20belief%20is%20found%20across%20all%20the%20religions%20and%20regions%20of%20Indian%20society%3B%20and%20the%20poorer%20the%20region%2C%20the%20stronger%20the%20belief%20seems%20to%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaturally%2C%20there%20are%20countermeasures%20to%20tackle%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20evil%20eye%20or%20wade%20off%20the%20evil%20eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBabies%20are%20smeared%20with%20kohl%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekatuka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Telugu%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Tamil%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekajal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Hindi)%20on%20their%20cheeks%2C%20eyes%2C%20forehead%2C%20palms%20and%20feet.%20An%20armlet%20made%20of%20black%20beads%20is%20also%20tied.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20portrait%20with%20a%20black%20face%2C%20horns%2C%20and%20a%20big%20moustache%20with%20its%20tongue%20out%20is%20placed%20in%20front%20of%20new%20and%20old%20houses.%20A%20large%20pumpkin%2C%20with%20the%20same%20face%20painted%20on%20it%2C%20is%20tied%20in%20front%20of%20a%20house.%20A%20white%20stone%20or%20a%20conch%20shell%20wrapped%20in%20a%20black%20thread%20may%20also%20be%20used.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20newly%20married%20couple%20or%20children%20who%20are%20doing%20well%20in%20life%20are%20welcomed%20into%20the%20house%20by%20making%20them%20go%20through%20the%20ritual%20of%20wading%20off%20the%20evil%20eye%20with%20the%20help%20of%20red%20liquid%20(%3Cem%3Eaalam%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Tamil).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20places%20of%20businesses%20make%20it%20a%20habit%20to%20wade%20off%20the%20evil%20eye%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20day%20of%20no%20moon%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20coconuts%2C%20lemons%20or%20pumpkins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20backs%20of%20vehicles%2C%20phrases%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eura%20nazar%20wala%20tera%20mu%20kala%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Blacken%20the%20face%20of%20those%20with%20an%20evil%20eye)%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENannu%20choosi%20edavaku%20ra%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Do%20not%20look%20at%20me%20and%20weep%20it)%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENee%20edupe%20na%20edugudhala%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(The%20more%20you%20cry%2C%20the%20more%20I%20will%20prosper).%20Or%20a%20lemon%20with%20a%20few%20green%20mirchis%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20bonnet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ERituals%20with%20rock%20salt%2C%20eggs%2C%20red%20mirchi%2C%20an%20old%20broomstick%20and%20burning%20an%20old%20oil-dipped%20cloth%20are%20also%20conducted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31184333%2F833211644_0bbf2db64b_h.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31184333%2F833211644_0bbf2db64b_h.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31184333%2F833211644_0bbf2db64b_h-300x230.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31184333%2F833211644_0bbf2db64b_h-1024x785.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682766%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22920%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVarious%20charms%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20ward%20off%20the%20evil%20eye.%20Photo%3A%20thaths%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%20NC%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESocial%20implications%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EScholars%20of%20structural%20functionalism%20in%20anthropology%20believe%20that%20every%20cultural%20trait%20and%20institution%20has%20some%20significance%20within%20a%20community.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20either%20wither%20away%20or%20transform%20into%20another%20cultural%20aspect.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20evil%20eye%20also%20has%20social%20implications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20could%20argue%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20evil%20eye%20can%20have%20some%20positive%20effects%2C%20like%20keeping%20a%20check%20on%20people%20who%20like%20to%20show%20off%20their%20wealth%20and%20success.%20From%20childhood%2C%20we%20are%20trained%20not%20to%20boast%20about%20anything%20but%20to%20be%20humble%20%E2%80%93%20to%20not%20attract%20any%20evil%20eyes.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20never%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20doing%20extremely%20well%E2%80%9D%20in%20our%20life.%20Rather%2C%20we%20say%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Aap%20ki%20dua%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Your%20blessings)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EChal%20raha%20hain%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%20(It%20is%20going%20alright).%20Never%20be%20arrogant%2C%20show%20public%20affection%2C%20and%20never%20boast%20about%20your%20wealth%2C%20beauty%2C%20health%20or%20success.%20However%2C%20these%20beliefs%20are%20prevalent%20only%20among%20the%20poor%20and%20middle%20class.%20The%20neo-rich%2C%20fuelled%20by%20neoliberalism%2C%20do%20not%20hesitate%20to%20flaunt%20their%20wealth%20and%20privilege.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20also%20downsides%20to%20this%20belief.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3ESowing%20animosity%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20develops%20distrust%20and%20animosity%20against%20one%E2%80%99s%20neighbours%20and%20relatives.%20Often%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20the%20power%20to%20place%20an%20evil%20eye%20on%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EAgainst%20scientific%20temper%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Belief%20in%20the%20evil%20eye%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20scientific%20temper%20that%20independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20founding%20leaders%20aspired%20to%20inculcate%20in%20the%20masses.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20normalisation%20of%20the%20belief%20and%20widespread%20practices%20to%20wade%20off%20the%20evil%20eye%20may%20see%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20practice%20for%20many%20generations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EEscaping%20responsibility%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20We%20are%20culturally%20trained%20to%20dodge%20responsibility%20of%20our%20life%20events%20and%20instead%20base%20them%20on%20various%20cosmic%20(planets%2C%20stars%20and%20time)%20and%20non-cosmic%20(cats%2C%20sneezing%2C%20evil%20eye%20and%20omens)%20entities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3EGood%20for%20religious%20business%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20widespread%20belief%20in%20the%20evil%20eye%20acts%20helps%20the%20thriving%20business%20of%20modern-day%20godmen%20and%20babas%2C%20who%20suggest%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparihar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epoojas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20remedies%20to%20protect%20oneself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20widespread%20belief%20in%20the%20evil%20eye%20resonates%20with%20the%20binaries%20that%20are%20socialised%20in%20culture.%20Though%20many%20Hindu%20religious%20scholars%20argue%20that%20Hinduism%20is%20beyond%20the%20binaries%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20inherently%20categorise%20our%20worldview%20in%20binaries.%20There%20is%20good%20and%20bad%20within%20all%20of%20us%3B%20similarly%2C%20there%20are%20good%20and%20bad%20people%20around%20us.%20Deities%20can%20protect%20us%20but%20also%20harm%20us%20when%20angered.%20Tapping%20into%20the%20sentiments%20of%20binaries%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20portrayed%20himself%20as%20a%20saviour%20of%20the%20masses%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20magic%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20politics%20share%20similarities%20with%20the%20downsides%20of%20the%20evil%20eye%20mentioned%20above.%20The%20party%20too%20seeks%20votes%20by%20sowing%20animosity%20between%20various%20groups.%20It%20has%20created%20and%20sustains%20a%20discourse%20against%20those%20who%20are%20rational%2C%20critical%20and%20believers%20in%20science.%20The%20BJP%20has%20not%20once%20owned%20the%20responsibility%20for%20its%20mishandling%20of%20state%20affairs%20and%20believes%20it%20is%20always%20right%20and%20others%20are%20wrong.%20Its%20politics%20has%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20with%20religion%2C%20which%20it%20immensely%20benefits%20from.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20both%20the%20belief%20in%20the%20evil%20eye%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20conception%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99%20that%20could%20cause%20harm%20stem%20deeply%20from%20belief%20and%20manifest%20into%20their%20construct.%20All%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20evil%20eye%20and%20the%20BJP%20consider%20the%20enemy%20real%20and%20act%20accordingly.%20Funnily%20enough%2C%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20evil%20eye%20and%20BJP%2C%20do%20not%20consider%20themselves%20as%20the%20source%20of%20bad%20things%20but%20strongly%20believe%20that%20%E2%80%98others%E2%80%99%20are%20placing%20the%20evil%20eye%20or%20harming%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERiding%20the%20wave%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20world%20and%20Indian%20politics%20have%20witnessed%20two%20kinds%20of%20leaders.%20The%20first%20rides%20the%20wave%20by%20speaking%20the%20political%20language%20that%20caters%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20primordial%20sentiments%20and%20beliefs%20of%20the%20masses.%20The%20second%20tells%20the%20masses%20that%20they%20were%20wrong%20(if%20they%20were)%20and%20intends%20to%20bring%20change%20in%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHitler%20found%20it%20easy%20to%20kindle%20and%20sustain%20hatred%20by%20fueling%20stereotypes%20against%20Jews%2C%20rose%20to%20power%20and%20oversaw%20the%20Holocaust.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20we%20have%20Nelson%20Mandela%2C%20who%2C%20after%20becoming%20the%20president%20of%20post-apartheid%20South%20Africa%2C%20requested%20all%20his%20countrymen%20to%20work%20together%20to%20make%20their%20country%20a%20rainbow%20nation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20India%2C%20we%20have%20the%20example%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20spoke%20against%20the%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20(but%20not%20against%20the%20caste%20system)%20and%20preached%20religious%20harmony%20when%20two%20communities%20were%20baying%20for%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20blood.%20Tagore%20went%20toured%20Japan%20and%20the%20US%2C%20where%20he%20said%20their%20conception%20of%20%E2%80%98nationalism%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20time%20of%20World%20War%20II%20was%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20made%20the%20easy%20choice%20of%20riding%20the%20wave.%20It%20will%20do%20so%20until%20the%20tides%20are%20in%20its%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESipoy%20Sarveswar%20teaches%20anthropology%20at%20Visva-Bharati%2C%20Santiniketan.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40SSarveswar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698758957000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31184258%2Fevil-eye.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhindutva-politics-evil-eye-daily-culture-masses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20angles%20have%20been%20investigated%20to%20explain%20the%20BJP's%20electoral%20success%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%20One%20aspect%20that%20has%20not%20been%20examined%20is%20the%20crucial%20role%20that%20the%20daily%20culture%20of%20the%20masses%20plays%20in%20helping%20certain%20political%20ideologies%20thrive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhindutva-politics-evil-eye-daily-culture-masses%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Punches%2C%20Kicks%20Fly%20As%20Mob%20Thrashes%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Cop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20cop%20was%20gheraoed%20and%20pummelled%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20showed%20a%20disturbing%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Mahoba%2C%20some%20260%20kilometre%20from%20state%20capital%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20boy%20was%20run%20over%20by%20a%20speeding%20bus%20and%20the%20cop%20had%20come%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%20It%20was%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20showed%20the%20video%2C%20that%20the%20crowd