treating%20patients%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20in%20the%20corridors%2C%20and%20in%20alleyways.%20Due%20to%20depleted%20stocks%20of%20anesthesia%20and%20oxygen%20and%20with%20no%20promise%20of%20new%20stocks%20coming%20in%2C%20he%20says%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20perform%20surgeries%20without%20anesthesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20buildings%20reduced%20to%20rubble%20and%20no%20one%20picking%20up%20piles%20of%20garbage%20for%20days%20on%20end%2C%20he%20says%20infections%20have%20already%20started%20spreading%20in%20Gaza.%20Lack%20of%20drinking%20water%20is%20spiking%20renal%20infections%2C%20and%20local%20authorities%20are%20forced%20to%20supply%20only%20highly%20salinated%20sea%20water%20to%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr.%20Elessi%20says%20more%20than%20supplying%20food%20and%20medicine%20to%20Gazans%2C%20the%20world%20must%20immediately%20stop%20this%20war.%20He%20specifically%20urges%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine.%20The%20below%20is%20full%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20lightly%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%E2%80%99re%20joined%20today%20by%20Dr%20Khamis%20Elessi%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20doctor%20and%20a%20specialist%20in%20pain%20management%20and%20rehabilitation.%20He%20joins%20us%20from%20Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Dr.%20Elessi%2C%20can%20I%20start%20by%20asking%20you%2C%20first%20tell%20me%20what%20are%20conditions%20like%20in%20the%20Shifa%20Hospital%20from%20where%20you%E2%80%99re%20joining%20us%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYeah%2C%20Shifa%2C%20first%20of%20all%2C%20Shifa%20Hospital%20is%20located%20in%20Gaza%20City.%20It%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20Gaza%20City.%20Yeah%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20Gaza%20City.%20Yeah%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Shifa%20hospital%20is%20very%2C%20very%20dramatic.%20Shifa%20Hospital%20is%20the%20biggest%20hospital%20in%20Palestine%20and%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20with%20more%20than%20700%20beds%20capacity.%20It%20is%20the%20main%20provider%20of%20healthcare%20for%20almost%2070%25%20to%2080%25%20of%20all%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPalestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20this%20hospital%20is%20providing%20acute%20care%20and%20chronic%20care%20for%20all%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epatients%2C%20including%20patients%20who%20have%20renal%20dialysis%20and%20patients%20who%20need%20surgery%20and%20other%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FuF3lPVIFsVk%3Fsi%3DHVqy8uF-uWDuJ0Jj%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnfortunately%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20war%2C%20Gaza%20hospitals%20had%20zero%20stocks%20of%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20all%20essential%20drugs.%20That%20was%20before%20the%20war%20but%20after%20the%20war%2C%20the%20situation%20even%20got%20worse.%20So%20the%20remaining%2050%25%20is%20also%20absent%20and%20with%20the%20closure%20of%20all%20borders%2C%20all%20inlets%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGaza%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20becoming%20very%2C%20very%20dire%2C%20with%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20casualties%20that%20have%20been%20caused.%20Whatever%20remains%20of%20the%20disposables%20medicines%2C%20and%20medical%20devices%20doctors%20are%20running%20in%20very%2C%20very%20primitive%20ways%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20managing%20acute%20pains%2C%20acute%20injuries%2C%20and%20these%20things.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20this%20moment%2C%20we%20have%20more%20than%207200%20individuals%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20more%20than%2018%2C500%20who%20were%20injured%2C%20let%20alone%20the%201%2C600%20people%20who%20are%20still%20missing%20under%20the%20rubble.%20Till%20this%20moment%20we%20have%20more%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethan%201%2C600%20Palestinians%20or%20even%20more%20still%20missing%20under%20the%20rubble%20of%20their%20homes.%20Why%3F%20Because%20there%20is%20no%20fuel%20for%20cars%20or%20big%20bulldozers%20to%20remove%20the%20debris%2C%20there%20are%20no%20lights%2C%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20water%2C%20no%20nothing%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20dangerous%20for%20civil%20defence%20and%20ambulances%20to%20reach%20these%20houses%20because%20they%20will%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebombed%2C%20unfortunately.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20first%20Dr.%20Elessi%2C%20how%20many%20people%20are%20sheltering%20in%20the%20Shifa%20Hospital%20and%20how%20many%20patients%20do%20you%20have%20as%20against%20the%20capacity%20officially%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20have%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20capacity%20of%20Shifa%20Hospital%20is%20full.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20overflowing.%20In%20fact%2C%20yesterday%20I%20witnessed%20that%20all%20doctors%20in%20the%20emergency%20department%20were%20treating%20their%20patients%20on%20the%20ground%20because%20so%20many%20patients%20are%20coming%20with%20no%20beds%20to%20care%20for%20them%2C%20and%20within%20the%20corridors%2C%20within%20the%20walls%2C%20within%20the%20parks%20of%20the%20hospital%20there%20are%20between%2020%2C000%20and%2030%2C000%20individuals%20who%20are%20sheltering%20inside%20the%20hospital.%20Why%3F%20Simply%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20a%20tiny%20piece%20of%20land%20for%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebeloved%20viewers%20in%20India%20and%20elsewhere.%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20area%20worldwide%20with%20a%20density%20percentage%20of%20around%205%2C700%20individuals%20per%20square%20kilometers%2C%20so%20it%20is%20more%20dense%20than%20China%2C%20more%20dense%20than%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20dense%20than%20New%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20me%20continue%20this%20point%2C%20so%202.3%20million%2C%20when%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20move%20from%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20Gaza%20to%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20Gaza%2C%20many%20people%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20tried%20to%20go%20there%20but%20we%20found%20that%20the%20shelling%20and%20bombing%20in%20that%20areas%20is%20even%20more%20intense%20than%20Gaza%20and%20we%20decided%2C%20%E2%80%98okay%20we%20will%20just%20go%20to%20a%20safer%20place%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%99%20and%20we%20will%20go%20back%20to%20our%20homes%20which%20is%20maybe%2C%20could%20be%20away%20from%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehelling.%20But%2C%20unfortunately%20shelling%20is%20everywhere%20and%20killing%20is%20everywhere%2C%20so%20people%20are%20running%20away%20for%20their%20lives.%20Almost%20125%2C000%20tons%20of%20ammunition%20have%20been%20dropped%20in%20Gaza%20which%20is%20a%20tiny%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20only%20360%20square%20kilometers%20area.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20me%20just%20clarify%20you%20said%20that%20initially%2C%20you%20moved%20from%20the%20north%2C%20from%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaza%20City%20to%20the%20South%20but%20because%20the%20shelling%20to%20the%20South%20was%20continuing%2C%20you%20weren%E2%80%99t%20safe%20and%20you%20had%20nowhere%20to%20stay.%20You%20went%20back%20to%20Gaza%20and%20I%20should%20correct%20myself%2C%20the%20Shifa%20hospital%20is%20in%20Gaza%20City%20not%20in%20Khan%20Yunis.%20You%20returned%20to%20the%20north%2C%20is%20that%20right%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20actually%20I%20moved%20four%20places%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20residing%20in%20Tel%20al-Hawa.%C2%A0%20I%E2%80%99m%20residing%20in%20%3Cstrong%3ETel%20al-Hawa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20the%20Tel%20al-Hawa%20or%20Rimal%20neighbourhood%20was%20completely%20devastated%20by%20the%20bombing%20of%20those%20High%20Towers%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20living%20in%20the%20center%20of%20that%20area%2C%20which%20is%20an%20area%20you%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewould%20say%20for%20the%20elite.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20modern%20area%20for%20people%20who%20are%20professionals%2C%20who%20are%20educated%2C%20who%20are%20well-off.%20So%20they%20reside%20in%20this%20area%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20that%20area%20was%20completely%20devastated%2C%20including%20the%20square%20of%20the%20President%20himself%2C%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas.%20We%20have%20a%20square%20near%20our%20home%20called%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Intersection%20where%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20home%20is.%20There%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20five%20minutes%20from%20our%20place%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20that%20area%20was%20completely%20devastated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18013311%2FF8qMGsubQAA8SRW.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22979%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18013311%2FF8qMGsubQAA8SRW.jpeg%20979w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18013311%2FF8qMGsubQAA8SRW-245x300.jpeg%20245w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18013311%2FF8qMGsubQAA8SRW-835x1024.jpeg%20835w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680542%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photograph%20purported%20to%20be%20of%20the%20fire%20burning%20at%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20after%20an%20airstrike%20killed%20500.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%2025%20towers%20and%20buildings%20were%20demolished%20so%20we%20ran%20away%20to%20our%20old%20home%2C%20my%20old%20home%20and%20all.%20Also%2C%20the%20shelling%20was%20very%2C%20very%20intense.%20Their%20deaths%20are%20in%20the%20hundreds%2C%20so%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20middle%20zone%20of%20Gaza%2C%20thinking%20that%20it%20will%20be%20safer%20and%20we%20found%20that%20the%20shelling%20is%20even%20worse.%20So%20I%20decided%20I%E2%80%99d%20go%20back%20and%20live%20with%20my%20family%20in%20our%20original%20home.%20But%20from%20time%20to%20time%20I%E2%80%99m%20coming%20here%20to%20Shifa%20to%20assist%20my%20friends%20in%20caring%20for%20acutely%20ill%20patients.%20Our%20colleagues%20have%20been%20extremely%20exhausted%2C%20imagine%20working%20for%2020%20days%20straight%20with%20no%20break%2C%20no%20stop%2C%20dealing%20with%20more%20than%2022%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20me%2C%20while%20the%20line%20exists%2C%20ask%20you%20a%20few%20specific%20questions%20so%20you%20can%20give%20me%20a%20few%20specific%20answers.%20Do%20you%20have%20things%20like%20anesthesia%20and%20oxygen%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20workable%20operating%20theaters%20or%20is%20all%20of%20that%20shut%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20hospitals%2C%20they%20still%20have%20some%20anesthesia%2C%20especially%20for%20operations.%20B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eut%20for%20milder%20operations%2C%20they%20do%20it%20without%20anesthesia%2C%20unfortunately.%20Because%20there%20is%20too%20much%20pressure%20and%20there%20are%20no%20available%20devices%2C%20no%20available%20medicines%20to%20care%20for%20patients%20in%20the%20corridors.%20This%20is%20one%20thing.%20In%20other%20hospitals%2C%20they%20run%20out%20of%20sutures%20to%20close%20wounds%20because%20Israelis%20are%20using%20these%20kind%20of%20sophisticated%20weapons%20that%20causes%20hundreds%20of%20cut-wounds%20in%20the%20body%20just%20like%20cutting%20the%20bodies%20into%20pieces%2C%20which%20consumes%20all%20the%20suture%20and%20causes%20severe%20burns.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20so%20many%20cases%20and%20also%20was%20told%20by%20many%20of%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esenior%20friends%20who%20work%20with%20burns%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20they%20see%20such%20kinds%20of%20burns%20and%20damage%20to%20the%20skin.%20The%20skin%20is%20cut%20into%20pieces%20just%20like%20you%20cut%20it%20with%20a%20knife%20and%20burned%20completely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20they%20using%20phosphorus%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20any%20signs%20of%20phosphorus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20using%20phosphorus%20and%20there%20are%20so%20many%20witnesses.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20it%20for%20myself.%20I%20cannot%20confirm%20it%20myself%20but%20we%20have%20so%20many%20witnesses%20and%20so%20many%20doctors%20who%20confirm%20that%20they%20have%20dealt%20with%20cases%20of%20white%20phosphorus.%20Actually%2C%20to%20be%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehonest%2C%20in%202009%20I%20published%20a%20paper%20in%20the%20Cochrane%20Library%2C%20talking%20about%20phosphorus%20and%20the%20injuries%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20with%20some%20of%20the%20patients%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20description%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20in%202009%20and%202012.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20I%20can%20see%20that%20at%20the%20moment%20you%20have%20electricity%20but%20how%20often%20does%20Shifa%20Hospital%20have%20electricity%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20do%20you%20have%20clean%20water%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOkay%2C%20Shifa%20Hospital%20has%20no%20electricity%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20running%20on%20generators.%20Unfortunately%2C%20within%2024%20hours%20or%2040-48%20hours%2C%20electricity%20will%20be%20shut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edown%20and%20no%20more%20patients%20will%20be%20admitted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20what%20about%20water%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20clean%20water%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20no%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20we%20are%20drinking.%20This%20is%20actually%20a%20point%20I%20wanted%20to%20raise.%20Yes%2C%20we%20have%207%2C000%20patients%20who%20were%20killed%2C%207%2C000%20victims%20who%20were%20murdered%20and%2020%2C000%20people%20who%20were%20injured%20with%20their%20kids%20and%20their%20families.%20But%20we%20have%20300%2C000%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20dying%20in%20silence%20because%20they%20suffer%20from%20chronic%20illnesses%20and%20need%20their%20care.%20But%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethey%E2%80%99re%20not%20receiving%20it%20because%20of%20the%20inability%20to%20access%20hospital%20care%20in%20the%20primary%20health%20care%20centers.%20Inability%20to%20come%20to%20hospitals%20in%20the%20main%20hospitals%2C%20inability%20to%20commute%20because%20there%20are%20no%20cars%20and%20everybody%20is%20scared%20for%20their%20life.%20This%20is%20one%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL-300x140.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL-1024x476.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22558%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestroyed%20buildings%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20thing%20just%20yesterday%20the%20mayor%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Nizar%20Hijazi%2C%20announced%20that%20because%20there%20is%20no%20water%20in%20Gaza%2C%20they%20have%20decided%20to%20use%20seawater.%20See%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20highly%20salinated%20water.%20There%20is%20no%20water%20in%20our%20aquifer%2C%20so%20decided%20they%20would%20use%20these%20wells%20which%20were%20closed%2010%20years%20ago%20because%20of%20the%20high%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esalinity%2C%20and%20high%20salt%20content.%20They%20decided%2C%20okay%2C%20we%20will%20open%20it%20for%20the%20people.%20This%20poses%20a%20high%20danger%20for%20people%20to%20cause%20renal%20failure%20and%20many%20problems%20in%20their%20blood%20because%20of%20the%20high%20salinity%20of%20this%20water.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20fuel%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sewage%20management%2C%20so%20they%20are%20directly%20bumping%20this%20sewage%20water%20and%20dirty%20water%20into%20the%20sea%20which%20causes%20pollution%20of%20the%20sea%2C%20killing%20marine%20life.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20third%20thing%20is%20that%20cancer%20patients%20who%20need%20this%20chemotherapy%20and%20radiotherapy%20are%20not%20receiving%20it.%20We%20have%2011%2C000%20patients%20with%20adrenal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eneeds%20who%20need%2C%20sorry%2C%201%2C200%20patients%20who%20need%20regular%20renal%20dialysis%20and%20they%20are%20not%20receiving%20it%20regularly.%20So%20this%20poses%20a%20danger%20to%20their%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20you%20said%20in%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20fuel%20at%20Shifa%20Hospital%20will%20stop.%20What%20then%20will%20happen%20to%20babies%20in%20incubators%3F%C2%A0%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20people%20on%20ventilators%3F%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20people%20who%20need%20dialysis%2C%20are%20they%20all%20destined%20to%20die%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20them%20will%20d