hich%20pose%20environmental%20hazards%20to%20people.%20We%20have%20people%20lining%20up%20for%20bread%20at%20bakeries.%20For%20lines%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20400%20individuals%2C%20500%20individuals%20falling%20in%20line%20just%20to%20get%20one%20bag%20of%20bread%20to%20feed%20their%20families%2C%20people%20are%20falling%20in%20lines%20just%20to%20get%20one%20bottle%20of%20water%20for%202%20hours%2C%203%20hours.%20So%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20disastrous.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20want%20to%20use%20this%20this%20time%20to%20send%20a%20message%20through%20your%20kind%20channel%20that%20the%20people%20here%2C%20despite%20their%20hunger%2C%20their%20thirst%2C%20do%20not%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewant%20only%20food%20or%20water%2C%20they%20want%20the%20war%20to%20stop.%20I%20hope%20that%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20use%20its%20influence%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20onslaught%20because%20people%20who%20are%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edying%20are%20civilians.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20if%20Israel%20will%20fight%20militants%20and%20they%20fight%20each%20other%20for%20years%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20paying%20the%20prices%20are%20the%20children%2C%20you%20see.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThousands%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethousands%20upon%20thousands%2C%20they%20received%20cuts%2C%20one%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20removed%2C%20skulls%20removed%2C%20these%20are%20very%2C%20very%20dramatic%2C%20very%20emotional%20when%20you%20see%20kids.%20We%20have%2069%20families%20who%20have%20been%20completely%20wiped%20out%20from%20the%20civil%20registry%20%E2%80%93%20what%20we%20need%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20food%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20need%20food%2C%20we%20need%20water%2C%20we%20need%20electricity%20but%20we%20need%20to%20stop%20this%20slaughter%20now%20and%20stop%20it%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr.%20Elessi%2C%20tell%20me%20what%20is%20the%20sort%20of%20destruction%20done%20by%20the%20air%20strikes%3F%20Are%20large%20parts%20of%20where%20you%20are%20demolished%3F%20Is%20it%20just%20rubble%2C%20have%20buildings%20been%20demolished%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20you%20go%20in%20Gaza%2C%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20homes%20have%20been%20demolished%2C%20more%20than%20200%2C000.%20So%20you%20go%20everywhere%2C%20whole%20squares%2C%20whole%20blocks%20are%20devastated.%20In%20fact%2C%20yesterday%20they%20attacked%20one%20block%2C%20killing%20300%20individuals%20in%20less%20than%2010%20seconds.%20Seven%20buildings%20have%20been%20completely%20dropped%20on%20top%20of%20their%20residences%2C%20killing%20till%20now%20they%20have%20retrieved%20120%20bodies%20and%20they%20say%20there%20are%20still%20more%20than%20120%20or%20150%20bodies%20underneath%20the%20rubble.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20they%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edon%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20equipment%20to%20remove%20these%20rubble%20there%20are%20many%20people%20who%20are%20trapped%20under%20the%20rubble%20who%20may%20be%20alive%20but%20will%20die%20under%20the%20rubble.%20Exactly%20because%20some%20of%20them%20have%20been%20trapped%20there%20for%20more%20than%2010%20days%20and%20now%20they%20die%20of%20hunger%20and%20suffocation.%20This%20fumes%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20fire%20made%20by%20these%20huge%20bombs.%20The%20bombs%2C%20my%20dear%2C%20are%20making%20gigantic%20sounds%2C%20supersonic%20explosions%20that%20even%20can%20stop%20the%20heart.%20We%20have%20many%2C%20many%20people%20who%20come%20with%20cardiac%20arrest%20just%20because%20there%20is%20too%20much%20scare%20and%20fear%20inside%20their%20hearts%20and%20they%20just%20fall%20down%20dead%2C%20right%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20this%2C%20Dr.%20Elessi%2C%20with%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20water%2C%20with%20electricity%20disappearing%20very%20quickly%2C%20with%20fuel%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20probably%20ending%2C%20and%20with%20garbage%20all%20around%2C%20is%20there%20a%20fear%20of%20disease%20spreading%3F%20Could%20you%20have%20epidemics%2C%20Cholera%2C%20for%20example%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20Health%20reported%20yesterday%20that%20they%20documented%20more%20than%204%2C500%20cases%20of%20skin%20diseases%20that%20are%20due%20to%20overcrowding.%20Actually%2C%20while%20you%E2%80%99re%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewalking%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20you%20can%20hear%20most%20of%20the%20kids%20coughing.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20an%20upsurge%20of%20respiratory%20tract%20infections%2C%20among%20all%20of%20them.%20And%20if%20one%20of%20them%20is%20infected%2C%20this%20will%20cause%20infection%20among%20thousands%20because%20they%20are%20backed%2C%20backed%20one%20next%20to%20the%20other%20people.%20Even%20this%20causes%20danger%20to%20the%20hospital%20itself%20because%20the%20hospital%20is%20no%20longer%20becoming%20a%20hygienic%20place.%20This%20will%20cause%20infection%20to%20the%20residents%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20seek%20refuge%20because%20the%20hospital%20itself%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20has%20most%20of%20the%20powerful%20potent%20germs%2C%20viruses%2C%20and%20bacteria.%20So%20those%20patients%20when%20they%20are%20seeking%20refuge%20inside%20the%20hospital%20corridors%20and%20in%20the%20parks%20and%20in%20the%20alleyways%20and%20roads.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%20at%20high%20risk%20of%20getting%20these%20infections%20and%20causing%20death%20indirectly%20to%20their%20friends%20and%20relatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20something%2C%20is%20it%20now%20impossible%20for%20people%20to%20have%20a%20daily%20bath%3F%20Has%20personal%20hygiene%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20conditions%20suffered%2C%20thus%20endangering%20people%20from%20that%20as%20well%20even%20doctors%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20doctors%2C%20they%20could%20barely%20go%20to%20the%20toilet%2C%20I%20mean%20once%20a%20day%20or%20maybe%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20a%20shower%20once%20every%205%20days%20or%206%20days%2C%20because%20there%20is%20no%20water%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lack%20of%20space%20for%20you.%20You%20go%20to%20your%20home%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20danger%20of%20being%20bombed%2C%20you%20go%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20you%20are%20in%20danger%20of%20being%20bombed.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20really%20hard%20and%20again%2C%20this%20will%20cause%20environmental%20hazards%20on%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20and%20their%20children%20and%20their%20families.%20Most%20families%20here%20have%20extended%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efamilies%2C%20so%20people%20gather%20together%2C%20the%20friends%2C%20the%20brothers%2C%20the%20sisters%2C%20all%20live%20in%20one%20place%20and%20then%20here%20comes%20the%20huge%2C%20two-ton%20bombs%20dropped%20on%20that%20building%20killing%20everybody%20inside%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eleaving%20a%20few%20people%20injured.%20But%20the%20rest%20will%20be%20killed%20underneath.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20worried%20are%20you%20about%20a%20ground%20invasion%20which%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20will%20happen%20but%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20when%3F%20Although%20it%E2%80%99s%20widely%20believed%2C%20it%20could%20be%20soon.%20How%20worried%20are%20people%20about%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20are%20so%20worrie%2C%20but%20they%20are%20more%20worried%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20humanity.%20They%E2%80%99re%20more%20worried%20about%20the%20absence%20of%20morals%20among%20world%20leaders%20when%20they%20said%20%E2%80%98okay%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20think%20about%20sending%20some%20food%20packages%20for%20the%20Gaza%20people%E2%80%99.%20Maybe%20tomorrow%2C%20maybe%20next%20week%2C%20always%20remember%20because%20I%20witnessed%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20when%20the%20first%20Ukrainian%20person%20was%20injured%2C%20two%20people%20were%20injured%2C%20The%20European%20Union%2C%20America%2C%20Britain%20opened%20their%20borders%20completely%2C%20gave%20Ukrainians%20all%20they%20need%2C%20gave%20them%20the%20money%2C%20gave%20them%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20food%2C%20gave%20them%20residence%2C%20gave%20them%20refuge%2C%20gave%20them%20shelter.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20in%20Gaza%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20closed%2C%20big%20prison%20and%20we%20are%20being%20bombed%20from%20the%20sea%2C%20land%2C%20and%20the%20earth.%20The%20sea%2C%20land%2C%20and%20earth%2C%20over%20the%20hour-%2024%2F7%2C%20this%20killing%20machine%20never%20stopped.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20me%2C%20I%20was%20trained%20in%20an%20Israeli%20Hospital%20one%20year%20in%202000%2C%20I%20spent%20one%20year%20in%20Sheba%20Medical%20Center%20and%20I%20have%20treated%20so%20many%20Israeli%20patients.%20They%20respected-%20those%20patients%20of%20mine%20and%20my%20Israeli%20teachers%2C%20they%20respected%20me%20and%20they%20think%20that%20we%20have%20so%20many%20friends%20in%20Palestine.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20those%20people%20who%20are%20thinking%20wisely%20and%20thinking%20like%20humans%20are%20few.%20Now%20the%20one%20who%20are%20calling%20for%20war%20and%20more%20killing%20is%20the%20extremist%2C%20far%20extremist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20last%20question%2C%20Dr.%20Elessi%2C%20in%20this%20traumatic%20situation%20how%20is%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20people%3F%20Like%20in%20Gaza%2C%20talk%20about%20those%20around%20you%2C%20what%20is%20their%20morale%20like%3F%20What%20is%20their%20spirit%20or%20are%20they%20beginning%20to%20lose%20hope%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20is%20the%20morale%3F%20The%20morale%20is%20high%20because%20we%20think%20if%20we%20die%2C%20we%20are%20martyrs.%20We%20will%20be%20going%20to%20heaven%20but%20un