Ffans-speculate-that-alia-bhatt-and-neetu-kapoor-celebrated-kanya-pujan-during-navratri-as-pic-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F104857061.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20Walks%20Out%20of%20Jail%2C%20TDP%20Reels%20From%20Decision%20to%20Not%20Contest%20Telangana%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31170949%2FF9w8PbHb0AAON-K.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20chief%20minister%20and%20president%20of%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20has%20walked%20out%20of%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20his%20party%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20told%20a%20team%20that%20called%20on%20him%20at%20the%20Rajahmundry%20Central%20Jail%20on%20October%2029%20that%20the%20TDP%20will%20not%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20has%20emerged%20the%20bigger%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Saturday%20delegation%20led%20by%20TDP%20Telangana%20president%20Kasani%20Gnaneshwar%20was%20told%20to%20keep%20away%20from%20the%20polls%20as%20poor%20performance%20by%20the%20party%20could%20dent%20its%20chances%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20elections%20due%20next%20year%2C%20on%20which%20Naidu%20asked%20leaders%20to%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20337px)%2085vw%2C%20337px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22337%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22278%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Naidu%20got%20bail%20from%20the%20AP%20high%20court%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20an%20alleged%20scam%20in%20the%20skill%20development%20programme%20taken%20up%20by%20his%20government%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20He%20is%20set%20to%20be%20released%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaidu%E2%80%99s%20stance%20on%20the%20Telangana%20polls%20met%20with%20wild%20reactions%20from%20party%20leaders%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Gnaneshwar%20himself%20tendered%20his%20resignation%20from%20his%20state%20post%20and%20also%20gave%20up%20his%20primary%20membership%20of%20the%20party.%20In%20an%20eight-page%20resignation%20letter%2C%20he%20accused%20Naidu%20of%20going%20back%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20give%20Gnaneshwar%20a%20free%20hand%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20party%20office%2C%20where%20Gnaneshwar%20arranged%20a%20meeting%20on%20his%20return%20from%20Rajahmundry%20to%20inform%20workers%20about%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20a%20large%20crowd%20revolted%20against%20the%20former%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20party%20contest%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20in%20its%2041-year%20existence%20as%20a%20political%20party%20that%20the%20TDP%20will%20skip%20an%20election%20to%20a%20state%20assembly%20or%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBarring%20a%20few%20instances%20when%20by-elections%20were%20held%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20caused%20by%20the%20killing%20of%20sitting%20MLAs%20of%20the%20rival%20Congress%20party%20by%20Naxalites%20and%20the%20TDP%20did%20not%20contest%20to%20express%20solidarity%20with%20slain%20victims%2C%20the%20party%20had%20never%20missed%20an%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecoveries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%2C%20consequently%2C%20took%20in%20its%20stride%20its%20worst%20ever%20electoral%20defeat%20when%20it%20lost%20the%20deposit%20in%20all%20the%2012%20assembly%20constituencies%20where%20by-elections%20were%20held%20in%20July%202010.%20These%20by-elections%20had%20been%20necessitated%20due%20to%20the%20resignation%20of%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20MLAs%20as%20part%20of%20their%20agitation%20for%20statehood%20to%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20Naidu%20forged%20a%20grand%20alliance%20with%20the%20then%20TRS%20%E2%80%93%20led%20by%20present%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%2C%20who%20steered%20the%20agitation%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Left%20parties%20to%20ensure%20the%20victory%20of%2015%20TDP%20MLAs%20in%20Telangana%20in%202014.%20Immediately%20after%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Telangana%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Telangana%20in%202018%2C%20Naidu%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20led%20a%20hectic%20campaign%20in%20the%20state%20that%20saw%20the%20victory%20of%20two%20party%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fortunes%20of%20the%20party%20started%20dipping%20with%20the%20desertion%20of%20all%20its%20MLAs%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20TRS%2C%20which%20is%20now%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaidu%20was%20booked%20by%20the%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20in%20the%20current%20case%20in%20which%20he%20has%20now%20got%20four%20week%20interim%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20petition%20seeking%20that%20proceedings%20against%20him%20be%20quashed%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20only%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20deadline%20for%20closure%20of%20nominations%20on%20November%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20partner%20in%20the%20elections%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20next%20year%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20party%20of%20actor-turned-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20contest%20elections%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20Jana%20Sena%20had%20staked%20claim%20for%20tickets%20to%2033%20seats%20initially%20but%20scaled%20it%20down%20to%2012%20later.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20conceded%20only%20six%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaucity%20of%20votes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kambhampati%20Ramamohan%20Rao%2C%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20and%20party%20coordinator%20for%20Telangana%2C%20the%20TDP%20also%20considered%20keeping%20away%20from%20the%20elections%20as%20a%20means%20of%20boycott%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20arrest%20of%20Naidu.%20He%20also%20asked%20whether%20it%20was%20required%20at%20all%20to%20enter%20the%20elections%20to%20earn%20only%20the%201%2C500%20to%202%2C000%20votes%20which%20the%20party%20polled%20in%20Huzurnagar%20and%20Nagarjunasagar%20assembly%20by-elections%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20be%20exploited%20by%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20CM%20and%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20arch%20rival%20Y.%20S.%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20to%20expose%20the%20hollowness%20of%20TDP.%20Moreover%2C%20where%20is%20the%20guarantee%20that%20the%20winners%20of%20TDP%20will%20remain%20with%20the%20party%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%2015%20MLAs%20who%20deserted%20the%20TDP%2C%20including%20present%20ministers%20E.%20Dayakar%20Rao%20and%20T.%20Srinivas%20Yadav%2C%20in%202014%2C%20and%20two%20other%20MLAs%20in%202018%2C%20there%20was%20massive%20erosion%20of%20its%20membership%2C%20right%20down%20to%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20after%20the%20movement%20for%20statehood%20to%20Telangana%20picked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20joined%20the%20TRS%20and%20secured%20plum%20posts%20in%20government%20and%20legislature%20since%202014.%20Ten%20days%20ago%2C%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20of%20TDP%2C%20Ravula%20Chandrasekhar%20Reddy%2C%20who%20was%20the%20last%20big%20name%20left%2C%20switched%20sides.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20state%20unit%20president%20L.%20Ramana%20was%20made%20an%20MLC%20of%20TRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20plight%20coincided%20with%20the%20centenary%20year%20of%20its%20patriarch%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20N.%20T.%20Rama%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGnaneshwar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaidu%20had%20made%20attempts%20to%20revive%20the%20party%20by%20holding%20a%20major%20public%20meeting%20in%20Khammam%20last%20year.%20It%20was%20followed%20up%20with%20wide-ranging%20consultations%20with%20available%20leaders%20at%20party%20offices.%20A%20huge%20public%20meeting%20was%20addressed%20by%20Naidu%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20foundation%20day%20at%20the%20Exhibition%20Grounds%20in%20Hyderabad%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Naidu%20picked%20Gnaneshwar%2C%20a%20backward%20classes%20leader%2C%20to%20head%20the%20state%20unit.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20state%20presidents%20of%20both%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20belong%20to%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20castes.%20Gnaneshwar%20himself%20addressed%20an%20impressive%20public%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20a%20%E2%80%98TDP%20%3Cem%3Esankharavam%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(sounding%20of%20the%20party%20bugle)%E2%80%99%20at%20Karimnagar%20when%20he%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20party%20leadership%20in%20Telangana%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGnaneshwar%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20informed%20Naidu%20on%20the%20190%20applications%20he%20had%20already%20received%20from%20aspirants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20hundreds%20of%20information%20technology%20professionals%20working%20in%20firms%20located%20in%20Hitech%20City%20of%20Hyderabad%20which%20was%20developed%20during%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministership%20in%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20protest%20against%20his%20arrest%20and%20subsequent%20shift%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%