lay%20regions%20and%20have%20succeeded%20in%20taking%20control%20of%20all%20the%20key%20trade%20routes%20between%20Myanmar%20and%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20an%20October%2030%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fopinion%2Fcommentary%2Fmyanmar-military-caught-off-guard-by-ethnic-alliances-northern-offensive.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Irawaddy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20trade%20routes%20with%20China%2C%20including%20the%20busiest%20border%20checkpoint%20in%20Muse%2C%20are%20now%20reportedly%20under%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20control%20and%20currently%20closed%20due%20to%20ongoing%20fighting.%20Chin%20Shwe%20Haw%2C%20a%20trading%20town%20that%20borders%20China%2C%20also%20fell%20to%20the%20insurgents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20is%20a%20tripartite%20military%20alliance%20comprising%20the%20Arakan%20Army%2C%20Ta%E2%80%99an%20National%20Liberation%20Army%20and%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20Army.%20Their%20respective%20armies%20have%20come%20together%20to%20launch%20simultaneous%20attacks%2C%20%E2%80%9Cstriking%20(Myanmarese%20military)%20regime%20targets%20and%20bases%20in%20several%20towns%20in%20the%20northern%20Shan%20state%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20report%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnalysts%20say%20the%20offensive%20surprised%20the%20regime%2C%20catching%20its%20military%20off%20guard.%20The%20military%20command%20in%20Naypyitaw%20failed%20to%20provide%20intelligence%20on%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20attacks%2C%20though%20they%20had%20prior%20warning%20that%20an%20operation%20was%20afoot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Alliance%20succeeded%20in%20capturing%20areas%20like%20Kutkai%2C%20Muse%2C%20Lashio%2C%20Namkham%2C%20Nawnghkio%20and%20Chin%20Shwe%20Haw%20in%20the%20northern%20Shan%20state%20and%20the%20ruby%20mining%20area%20of%20Mogoke%20in%20the%20upper%20Mandalay%20region.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20operation%20also%20blocked%20lucrative%20trade%20routes%20between%20China%20and%20Myanmar%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Lashio-Muse%20Highway%20and%20Lashio-Chin%20Shwe%20Haw%20Road%20%E2%80%93%20to%20prevent%20regime%20reinforcements%20from%20using%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20trade%20routes%20with%20China%2C%20including%20the%20busiest%20border%20checkpoint%20in%20Muse%2C%20are%20now%20reportedly%20under%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20control%20and%20currently%20closed%20due%20to%20ongoing%20fighting.%20Chin%20Shwe%20Haw%2C%20a%20trading%20town%20that%20borders%20China%2C%20also%20fell%20to%20the%20insurgents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMyanmar%20shares%20a%202%2C129-kilometre%20long%20border%20with%20China.%20In%20the%20last%20three%20and%20a%20half%20decades%2C%20Myanmar%20has%20developed%20a%20particularly%20strong%20business%20relation%20with%20China.%20According%20to%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%2C%20the%20bilateral%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20from%20April%202022%20to%20the%20middle%20of%20January%202023%20had%20touched%20%24%20159.412%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20dynamic%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20have%20witnessed%20several%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fexpert-speak%2Funderstanding-the-relations-between-myanmar-and-china%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20owing%20to%20the%20wariness%20of%20Myanmar%20authorities%20towards%20Chinese%20intent%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20weaponising%20ethnic%20groups%2C%20debt%20scares%2C%20or%2C%20unsustainable%20projects%20%E2%80%93%20the%20relationship%20has%20always%20maint