-protest-london-demand-gaza-ceasefire-2023-10-28%2F%5C%22%3Emajor%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20several%20European%20and%20American%20cities%20last%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20persistence%20of%20these%20public%20protests%20in%20several%20European%20and%20American%20cities%20has%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20Western%20governments%20by%20surprise%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20after%20an%20initial%20show%20of%20strong%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20when%20Western%20heads%20of%20government%20visited%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20stand%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%2C%20they%20are%20now%20%E2%80%9Cpeddling%20backwards%20pretty%20furiously%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20two%20developments%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20added%20to%20the%20size%20and%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20protests%20we%20have%20seen.%20For%20instance%2C%20around%20200%2C000%20people%20were%20peacefully%20protesting%20last%20weekend%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20developments%20are%3A%20first%2C%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20social%20media%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20can%20provide%20%E2%80%9Ca%20gut%20level%20of%20engagement%E2%80%9D%20with%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20as%20a%20result%20of%20three%20weeks%20of%20airstrikes%20and%20the%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20development%20is%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20diaspora%20as%20well%20as%20the%20size%20of%20the%20pro-Palestine%20sphere%20of%20population%20in%20European%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20people%20protesting%2C%20not%20just%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Washington%2C%20but%20also%20in%20London%20and%20Berlin%2C%20are%20Jewish.%20This%2C%20he%20suggests%2C%20is%20particularly%20noteworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20that%20there%20is%20a%20marked%20shift%2C%20as%20you%20go%20down%20the%20generations%2C%20over%20how%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20is%20viewed.%20Young%20Americans%20differ%2C%20often%20significantly%2C%20from%20their%20parents%20and%20grandparents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Democratic%20Party%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20position%20of%20strong%20support%20for%20Israel%20seems%20to%20be%20weakening%2C%20and%20possibly%2C%20fracturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mr.%20Rodenbeck%20spoke%20in%20detail%20about%20Germany%20and%20the%20German%20government%E2%80%99s%20very%20specific%20attitude%20to%20Israel%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%20just%20political.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20constitutional.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20emerging%20gap%20between%20how%20the%20German%20government%20views%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%20and%20how%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20population%20view%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20impact%20these%20protests%20in%20America%20and%20Europe%20will%20have%20on%20their%20respective%20home%20governments%2C%20on%20the%20Netanyahu%20government%20and%20public%20opinion%20in%20Israel%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Arab%20street%20and%2C%20more%20specifically%2C%20leaders%20like%20President%20El-Sisi%20of%20Egypt%20and%20King%20Abdullah%20of%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8oo8Yy4yxl8%3Fsi%3D7Xs6_3XN4jX2aDL5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698749149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31154552%2Fkt-31st-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-enough-is-enough-is-the-message-from-european-