3%20The%20Bookshop%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20close%20its%20doors%20under%20that%20famous%20counter-culture%20peace%20sign%20on%20October%2031.%20We%20are%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20so%20much%20more%20than%20a%20bookstore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134020%2FEzP4DtlVEAchdc9.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22807%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134020%2FEzP4DtlVEAchdc9.jpeg%20807w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134020%2FEzP4DtlVEAchdc9-300x249.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKD%20Singh%2C%20founder%20of%20The%20Bookshop.%20Photo%3A%20X%2FBookshopJB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EKD%20and%20Nini%20Singh%20opened%20The%20Bookshop%20in%20Jorbagh%20in%201971.%20Nini%20has%20always%20said%20that%20the%20Bookshop%20was%20her%20fourth%20child.%20Of%20her%20children%2C%20this%20was%20unsurprisingly%20the%20most%20like%20KD%3A%20laid%20back%2C%20relaxed%2C%20and%20yet%20full%20of%20surprises.%20One%20went%20in%20there%20for%20the%20books%20of%20course%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20jazz%2C%20the%20company%2C%20and%20for%20a%20chat%20with%20KD%20and%20Nini.%20The%20shop%20did%20not%20occupy%20a%20large%20space%20%E2%80%93%20just%20two%20aisles%20and%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20alcove%20at%20the%20back%20%E2%80%93%20so%20if%20a%20fair%20few%20had%20the%20same%20idea%20about%20craving%20some%20book%20talk%20and%20company%2C%20the%20aisles%20could%20fill%20up%20quite%20quickly.%20It%20was%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20a%20story%20about%20KD%E2%80%99s%20setting%20up%20The%20Book%20Mark%20in%20Calcutta%20might%20illuminate%20the%20atmosphere%20at%20The%20Bookshop.%20He%20was%20interviewing%20a%20young%20college%20graduate%20to%20help%20run%20the%20shop%20with%20my%20mother%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20name%20her%20favourite%20children%E2%80%99s%20authors.%20Nerves%20may%20have%20got%20the%20better%20of%20her%2C%20for%20she%20forgot%20to%20mention%20Enid%20Blyton.%20She%20got%20the%20job.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20KD%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20Enid%20Blyton%20or%20that%20none%20of%20her%20books%20were%20to%20be%20found%20at%20The%20Bookshop%20(they%20were)%3A%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20that%20he%20firmly%20believed%20that%20there%20was%20so%20much%20more%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20literature.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20395px)%2085vw%2C%20395px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134141%2FFxtk_lDWAAM0G_u-768x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134141%2FFxtk_lDWAAM0G_u-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134141%2FFxtk_lDWAAM0G_u-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134141%2FFxtk_lDWAAM0G_u.jpeg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682678%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22527%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Bookshop%2C%20Jorbagh.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BookshopJB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20it%20was%20that%20when%20kids%20went%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20corner%20at%20The%20Bookshop%2C%20they%20discovered%20new%20worlds.%20They%20were%20spoken%20with%20as%20equals%20and%20guided%20to%20new%20discoveries%2C%20new%20authors%2C%20a%20whole%20universe%20of%20possibilities.%20I%20always%20associate%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20corner%20with%20Nini%20%E2%80%93%20but%20that%20also%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20absolute%20joy%20she%20took%20in%20pulling%20out%20a%20book%20for%20a%20child%2C%20sitting%20down%20on%20a%20moora%20(stool)%20with%20them%20(in%20later%20years%2C%20there%20was%20often%20a%20cat%20who%20might%20have%20to%20be%20regretfully%20turfed%20off%20to%20make%20space)%2C%20and%20leading%20them%20into%20a%20literary%20adventure.%20Sonal%20Narain%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20managing%20partner%20soon%20after%20KD%E2%80%99s%20passing%20in%202014%2C%20kept%20up%20that%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20it%20boils%20down%20to%20treating%20those%20who%20entered%20the%20shop%20as%20people%20first.%20You%20went%20to%20The%20Bookshop%20to%20browse.%20For%20real%20book%20lovers%2C%20this%20was%20heaven.%20You%20took%20your%20time%3B%20if%20you%20wanted%20to%20chat%20and%20ask%20for%20recommendations%2C%20you%20could.%20If%20you%20wanted%20to%20be%20left%20alone%20with%20the%20books%2C%20that%20was%20fine%20too.%20But%20if%20you%20did%20ask%20for%20suggestions%2C%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20of%20possibilities%20would%20open%20up%2C%20because%20you%20weren%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20guided%20to%20the%20latest%20bestsellers.%20The%20recommendations%20depended%20on%20how%20you%20had%20been%20browsing%20before%2C%20and%20if%20you%20were%20a%20repeat%20customer%20(which%20most%20were)%2C%20what%20you%20usually%20looked%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20was%20reminded%20of%20this%20when%20Nini%20called%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20they%20had%20doubled%20the%20sales%20of%20my%20(only)%20book%20in%20the%20second%20month.%20And%20she%20knew%20exactly%20who%20had%20bought%20those%20two%20copies.%20The%20point%20of%20this%20is%20not%20to%20boast%20about%20my%20dizzying%20ascent%20up%20the%20bestseller%20list%2C%20but%20to%20illustrate%20something%20about%20Nini.%20She%20knew%20the%20people%20who%20came%20to%20her%20shop.%20She%20also%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20been%20pretty%20certain%20when%20one%20of%20those%20two%20customers%20had%20walked%20in%20that%20he%20would%20buy%20my%20book%20even%20before%20he%E2%80%99d%20picked%20it%20up%20because%20of%20his%20interests%20and%20career.%20(Being%20related%20to%20the%20proprietor%20got%20your%20book%20on%20the%20shelf%2C%20but%20familial%20relationships%20certainly%20did%20not%20extend%20to%20having%20your%20book%20promoted%20%E2%80%93%20the%20customer%20came%20first.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20old-fashioned%2C%20courteous%20world%20for%20an%20old-fashioned%20time.%20That%20era%20seems%20to%20be%20slipping%20out%20of%20our%20grasp%20even%20as%20I%20type.%20In%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%20of%20Amazon%20and%20online%20shopping%2C%20of%20bestseller%20lists%2C%20of%20glitzy%20promotions%20and%20furious%20underselling%2C%20this%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20world.%20The%20Bookshop%20did%20not%20put%20their%20stock%20online.%20How%20could%20they%20%E2%80%93%20they%20often%20only%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20copies%20of%20each%20book%20at%20any%20given%20time%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20stock%20as%20varied%20an%20inventory%20as%20possible.%20Often%2C%20when%20you%20bought%20a%20book%2C%20you%20were%20taking%20home%20the%20only%20copy%20in%20the%20shop.%20(If%20you%20went%20back%20the%20next%20day%2C%20it%20had%20been%20replaced.)%20But%20the%20eclecticism%20came%20at%20a%20price%3A%20cut-throat%20promotions%20and%20online%20sales%20were%20out%20of%20the%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20348px)%2085vw%2C%20348px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134257%2FFkGpvSvUcAEF5B2-225x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134257%2FFkGpvSvUcAEF5B2-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134257%2FFkGpvSvUcAEF5B2-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31134257%2FFkGpvSvUcAEF5B2.jpeg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682679%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22464%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Bookshop%2C%20Jorbagh.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BookshopJB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20closest%20KD%20came%20to%20a%20commercial%20venture%20was%20when%20he%20opened%20another%20Bookshop%20in%20Khan%20Market%20in%20the%201980s.%20The%20Khan%20Market%20shop%20had%20a%20slightly%20different%20feel%20%E2%80%93%20I%20put%20it%20down%20to%20half%20the%20crowd%20in%20there%20swooning%20over%20Rachna%2C%20his%20daughter%2C%20who%20helped%20run%20the%20place.%20It%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20also%20a%20more%20accessible%20and%20popular%20market.%20And%20lovelorn%20suitors%20aside%2C%20The%20Bookshop%20was%20still%20the%20place%20to%20be.%20Long%20after%20they%E2%80%99d%20been%20showered%20by%20stardust%2C%20Salman%20Rushdie%2C%20Vikram%20Seth%2C%20Arundhati%20Roy%20and%20others%20would%20continue%20to%20stop%20by%2C%20as%20did%20their%20readers.%20Quite%20often%2C%20the%20latter%20walked%20away%20with%20a%20signed%20copy.%20To%20KD%2C%20the%20college%20student%20in%20search%20of%20his%20latest%20Rushdie%20book%20was%20as%20important%20as%20the%20man%20himself.%20Contrarian%3F%20Perhaps.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20regulars%20returned%2C%20and%20returned%2C%20and%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Khan%20Market%20episode%20ended%20almost%20twenty-five%20years%20later%2C%20in%202006%2C%20when%20the%20lease%20ran%20out%2C%20and%20KD%20returned%20to%20Jorbagh%2C%20where%20Nini%20had%20kept%20the%20original%20going%2C%20with%20a%20brief%20hiatus%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9880s.%20The%20regulars%20followed%2C%20mostly.%20The%20Khan%20Market%20site%20became%20another%20jewellery%20store%2C%20or%20something.%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20Khan%20Market%E2%80%99s%20soul%20withered%20with%20the%20Bookhshop%E2%80%99s%20going%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20the%20signs%20were%20there.%20The%20times%20were%20changing%20and%20The%20Bookshop%20was%20already%20belonging%20to%20another%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20life%20went%20on%2C%20even%20after%20the%20rupture%20of%20KD%E2%80%99s%20passing%20in%202014.%20Covid%2C%20however%2C%20was%20a%20mountain%20too%20high%2C%20at%20least%20for%20Nini.%20The%20store%20had%20to%20adapt%20to%20survive.%20Sonal%20Narain%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20Khan%20Market%20shop%20in%202001%2C%20and%20was%20now%20managing%20partner%2C%20opted%20for%20some%20creative%20marketing.%20She%20and%20Mahika%20Chaturvedi%20took%20The%20Bookshop%20into%20the%20virtual%20space%2C%20but%20without%20putting%20their%20stock%20online.%20If%20you%20wanted%20a%20book%2C%20you%20emailed%20or%20called.%20A%20conversation%20ensued%2C%20and%20then%20books%2C%20having%20been%20jointly%20chosen%2C%20were%20despatched.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESonal%20will%20now%20take%20The%20Bookshop%20%E2%80%93%20under%20its%20new%20name%2C%20The%20Bookshop%20Inc%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20next%20stage%20of%20its%20journey.%20The%20new%20edition%20of%20this%20book%20love%20story%20will%20open%20its%20doors%20in%20Lodhi%20Colony%20on%20November%201%20%E2%80%93%20a%20new%20partnership%2C%20a%20new%20location%2C%20a%20new%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Nini%2C%20however%2C%20it%20is%20time%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20her%20fourth%20child.%20There%20have%20been%20wonderful%20moments%2C%20but%20now%20this%20child%20is%20ready%20to%20find%20her%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFarewell%2C%20Bookshop.%20Thank%20you%20for%20the%20books%2C%20the%20music%2C%20the%20companionship%2C%20the%20memories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPriyanjali%20Malik%20is%20an%20author%20and%20commentator%20who%20was%20lucky%20enough%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20a%20bookshop.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698748210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31133525%2FDy9o7MGX4AAhJM3.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%