f%20those%20who%20are%20%23MakingSportWork.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGanga%20and%20Jamana%20are%20twin%20sisters%20who%20come%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Ratlam%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Their%20journey%20with%20sports%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20one.%20Being%20residents%20of%20a%20conservative%20village%20in%20Ratlam%2C%20education%20was%20never%20a%20first%20choice%2C%20let%20alone%20indulging%20in%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20relentless%20persuasion%2C%20which%20went%20on%20for%20six%20months%2C%20their%20parents%20allowed%20the%20twins%20to%20join%20the%20%3Cem%3ENanhi%20Kali%3C%2Fem%3E%20after-school%20tuition%20centre%20run%20by%20the%20Naandi%20Foundation%2C%20where%20they%20received%20daily%20academic%20support.%20Soon%2C%20they%20took%20this%20opportunity%20to%20play%20sports%2C%20which%20was%20a%20part%20of%20this%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20demonstrated%20exceptional%20skill%20in%20sports%2C%20and%20were%20soon%20participating%20in%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20sports%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Toofaan%20Games.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20began%20in%202019%20when%20Rohini%20Mukherjee%2C%20the%20then%20head%20of%20Nanhi%20Kali%20operations%2C%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20introduce%20the%20girls%20to%20sports.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20fundamental%20life%20skills%20that%20school%20classrooms%20can%E2%80%99t%20teach%20you%20%E2%80%93%20leadership%2C%20teamwork%2C%20facing%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20And%20that%20is%20where%20sports%20came%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%201%2C90%2C000%20girls%2C%20including%20the%20twin%20sisters%2C%20get%20at%20least%2010%20years%20of%20schooling%20and%20are%20introduced%20to%20sports%20once%20they%20are%20enrolled%20in%20this%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%20In%20the%20current%20edition%20that%20started%20in%20August%202023%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20girls%20under%20their%20wing%20are%20competing%20right%20from%20the%20village%20level%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20nationals%20organised%20by%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20organisation%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooked%20to%20introduce%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20faced%20a%20challenge%20of%20not%20having%20anyone%20on%20the%20staff%20who%20could%20lead%20a%20sports-focused%20initiative.%20Fortunately%2C%20they%20found%20the%20right%20candidate%20in%20Lisa%20Murawsky%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20international%20sports%20consultant%2C%20educator%20and%20coach%20for%20over%2020%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohini%20(now%20the%20Head%20of%20Global%20Partnerships%20and%20Strategy)%20and%20Lisa%20together%20created%20the%20%E2%80%98Sports%20for%20Life%E2%80%99%20programme%20for%20the%20foundation%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20these%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333273%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Toofan%20Games%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20opportunities%20it%20brings%20to%20girls%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaandi%20Foundation%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20is%20an%20organisation%20working%20diligently%20since%20its%20conception%20in%201998%20towards%20the%20eradication%20of%20poverty%20and%20upliftment%20of%20girls%20and%20women%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20events%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20that%20the%20girls%20participate%20in%20are%20the%2050m%20sprint%2C%20shuttle%20run%2C%20standing%20long%20jump%2C%20and%20endurance%20run.%20These%20four%20events%20were%20selected%20because%20they%20are%20simple%2C%20easy%20to%20conduct%20and%20give%20the%20girls%20an%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20their%20speed%2C%20agility%2C%20lower%20body%20strength%20and%20stamina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%20130%20girls%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20each%20year%20and%20for%20many%20of%20them%2C%20the%20games%20are%20the%20first%20time%20they%20set%20foot%20outside%20their%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20point%20to%20emphasise%20here%20is%20that%20the%20initiative%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F101981%2Fuplabdhi-misha-chandola-teach-girls-project-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eled%20by%20women%20entirely%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20right%20from%20coaching%20to%20the%20results.%20The%20existing%20infrastructure%20at%20Naandi%20%E2%80%94%20under%20the%20Nanhi%20Kali%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20has%20propelled%20the%20movement%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Nanhi%20Kali%20after-school%20tuition%20centres%E2%80%99%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261243%2Fmalnutrition-orphanage-girl-child-hyderabad-women-donation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaged%20by%20a%20young%20woman%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20same%20community%20as%20the%20girls.%20When%20sports%20were%20introduced%2C%20these%20tutors%20were%20to%20deliver%20the%20weekly%20sports%20drills%20and%20practices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%20it%20was%20optional%20for%20tutors%20to%20become%20%E2%80%98sports%20allies%E2%80%99.%20About%20half%20of%20them%20said%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20was.%20By%20the%20second%20year%2C%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohini%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tutors%20initially%20went%20in%20not%20knowing%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20once%20they%20experienced%20it%2C%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20event%2C%20back%20in%202020%2C%20vindicated%20their%20belief%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20sports%20and%20physical%20activity%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%20organisation%20inculcating%20sports%20into%20their%20work%20and%20regular%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20videos%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20girls%20doing%20these%20sports%20drills%20were%20sent%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20WhatsApp%20to%20the%20sports%20allies.%20To%20streamline%20this%20process%20further%2C%20Naandi%20decided%20to%20create%20its%20own%20app%20called%20SportStar%20to%20create%20a%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20once%20a%20week%2C%20a%20video%20of%20a%20sports%20drill%20is%20sent%20out%20to%20roughly%206%2C000%20sports%20allies.%20This%20allows%20for%20feedback%20and%20collaboration%20among%20all%20of%20them%20as%20everyone%20shares%20their%20training%20videos%2C%20which%20ensures%20that%20the%20app%20has%20more%20content%20for%20their%20perusal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20girls%20cannot%20relate%20to%20YouTube%20videos%20of%20foreigners%20doing%20these%20drills.%20With%20this%20exchange%20of%20videos%2C%20we%20have%20ended%20up%20creating%20more%20resources%20for%20our%20girls%20to%20imbibe%20information%20from.%20The%20app%20is%20not%20open%20to%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohini.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20girl%20is%20doing%20some%20exercise%20well%2C%20then%20we%20use%20that%20video%20during%20our%20drills%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20organisation%20terms%20%E2%80%98Sports%20for%20Life%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Every%20young%20girl%20now%20enjoys%20one%20sports%20class%20per%20week%20where%20they%20not%20only%20play%20but%20also%20learn%20about%20body%20movement%2C%20nutrition%20and%20menstrual%20health%20management.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921.jpg%209