a%20football%20team%20for%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20football%20teams%20in%20turn%20led%20to%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20training%20programme%20for%20coaches.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20have%20women%20football%20coaches%20who%20have%20D-Level%20Certification%20in%20Coaching%20from%20the%20All-India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vyas%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20benefited%20personally.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20student%2C%20I%20played%20kabaddi%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekho%20kho%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20I%20was%20in%20my%20college%20team.%20But%20I%20never%20thought%20that%20sports%20would%20enter%20my%20life%20again%20and%20that%20it%20would%20enrich%20my%20work%20with%20the%20community.%20It%20has%20helped%20me%20improve%20my%20health.%20I%20also%20find%20it%20to%20be%20refreshing%2C%20it%20breaks%20any%20monotony%20that%20may%20come%20into%20my%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoornima%20Singh%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20programme%20in%20the%20Prayagraj%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20works%20with%207%2C856%20girls%2C%20along%20with%20271%20sports%20allies.%20She%20discovered%20that%20the%20girls%20did%20not%20need%20any%20motivation%20to%20play%20sports.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20ready%2024%C3%977%20to%20go%20to%20the%20playground%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20935px)%20100vw%2C%20935px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F264855944_457387342574540_7626058875127701234_n-1696415459.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20girls%20under%20the%20Nanhi%20Kali%20Project%20showing%20their%20notebooks%20to%20their%20teacher.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F264855944_457387342574540_7626058875127701234_n-1696415459.jpg%20935w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%